Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.00,0:00:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}片名：家庭阴谋{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.70,0:00:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}有人在这里{\r}\N[Speaking In A Girlish, Dreamy Voice] Someone is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.81,0:00:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不太靠近{\r}\NNot closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.51,0:00:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不太情愿{\r}\NNot willingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.48,0:00:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我感到了阻碍{\r}\NI feel a holding back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.22,0:00:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}有什么麻烦,亨利?{\r}\NWhat's the trouble, Henry?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.62,0:01:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}太多回忆,太多痛苦{\r}\N[In Deep Male Voice] Too many memories, too much pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.76,0:01:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}太多悲伤{\r}\NToo... much... sorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.90,0:01:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}无论和你在一起的是谁{\r}\N[In High Voice] Whoever is there with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.87,0:01:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}让他们说话,亨利{\r}\Ntell them to speak up, Henry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.64,0:01:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}让他们靠近一点{\r}\NTell them to come closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.81,0:01:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我想我知道那是谁,布兰琪夫人{\r}\N[Woman #2] I think I know who it is, Madame Blanche.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.65,0:01:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我想我知道是什么困扰着她{\r}\NI think I know what's bothering her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.68,0:01:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}"她",是吗? 别担心,兰伯特女士{\r}\N[In High Voice] Her, is it? Never you mind, Miss Rainbird.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.52,0:01:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}没有你的指示 亨利不会做任何事的{\r}\NI won't have you doing Henry's work for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.93,0:01:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}现在,让我们一起来吧,亲爱的 这就是为什么今晚我们在这里{\r}\NNow, let's have it, my love. That's why we're here tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.96,0:01:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}为了帮助我的朋友 摆脱她的痛苦{\r}\NTo help my friend be rid of her torment.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.90,0:01:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}她有休息的权力,让她疲惫的头脑 能在枕头上歇息,于每个晚上…{\r}\NShe has a right to rest her weary head on a pillow each night...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.84,0:01:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}平静地安睡,有如天使{\r}\Nand sleep the peaceful sleep of the angels.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.84,0:01:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你怎么知道我有睡眠的困扰?{\r}\NHow did you know about my troubled sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.08,0:02:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 谁告诉你的? - 她夜晚无法长睡{\r}\N- Who told you? - Her nights cannot go on like this much longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.62,0:02:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我从来没有告诉别人我的噩梦{\r}\NI never told a soul about my nightmares.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.85,0:02:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你怎么会… - 是谁来到这里…{\r}\N- How could you... - Who is this person who arrives...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.22,0:02:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}今晚我们的存在 所以才不敢靠近吗?{\r}\Nin our presence tonight, but does not dare to come close to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.16,0:02:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是她,是我的妹妹哈丽叶{\r}\NIt's her. It's my sister Harriet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.07,0:02:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 绝对是 - 她保持距离{\r}\N- It must be. - [In Henry's Voice] She stays her distance,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.50,0:02:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}朱莉亚・兰伯特 因为她没有感受到…{\r}\NJulia Rainbird, for she does not feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.24,0:02:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你的爱或是你的善意{\r}\Nyour love or your kindness yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.48,0:02:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你太自私了{\r}\NThere is selfishness where you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.78,0:02:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我已经什么都为她做了{\r}\NI've had all I can take from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.75,0:02:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}她每晚都来到我的梦中{\r}\NNight after night, coming into my dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.15,0:02:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}发牢骚,抱怨,努力使我感到内疚{\r}\NWhining, complaining, trying to make me feel guilty,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.42,0:02:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}就好像我需要她来告诉我是非{\r}\Nas though I need her to tell me right from wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.63,0:02:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}告诉她,我知道该怎么做{\r}\NTell her I know what has to be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.70,0:02:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我一直想这么做已经一年了{\r}\NI've been wanting to do it for a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.23,0:02:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但是我,朱莉亚・兰伯特 已经做出决定了{\r}\NBut it is I, Julia Rainbird, who has made the decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.84,0:03:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不需要她来鞭策我{\r}\N[Sighing] I don't need her to goad me on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.11,0:03:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他们在我梦中丑陋的话语 使我生病{\r}\NThey're making me ill with their ugly words in my ugly dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.18,0:03:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}告诉她该停止了 回去,不要管我{\r}\NTell her to stop it, to go away and leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.95,0:03:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}喔,不,不,别让她走!{\r}\N[Stammering] Oh, no. No, no. Don't let her go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.99,0:03:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 别让她离开 - 哈丽叶?{\r}\N- Don't let her go away. - Harriet?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.56,0:03:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}哈丽叶,留下来,哈丽叶{\r}\NHarriet, stay with us, Harriet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.73,0:03:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你姐姐要和你说话 从她的心灵深处{\r}\NYour sister wants to speak to you now, from the depths of her soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.17,0:03:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}怎么了? 怎么回事?{\r}\N- What's wrong? What is it? - [Wailing Continues]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.57,0:03:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}她说"我已经等了好久…"{\r}\NShe says, "I've waited so long...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.68,0:03:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}"想听到你说话,朱莉亚"{\r}\N"to hear from you, Julia.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.81,0:03:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}"没有你在,我很不快乐"{\r}\NI've been so unhappy without you."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.05,0:03:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是你,哈丽叶{\r}\NIt is you, Harriet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.99,0:03:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}喔,我很抱歉{\r}\NOh, I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.22,0:03:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不该让你那么做的{\r}\NI-I should never have made you do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.23,0:03:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}喔,都已经过去了{\r}\NOh, it's all past now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.23,0:03:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但是我会尽我所能地去弥补{\r}\NBut I'll do what I can to make up for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.67,0:04:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如果他还活着 我会找到你的儿子{\r}\NIf he's still alive, I'll find your son.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.00,0:04:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我会带他到我身边并且爱他{\r}\NAnd I'll take him in my arms and love him...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.04,0:04:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}有如我就是你 我可怜的哈利叶{\r}\Nas if I were you, my poor Harriet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.04,0:04:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我会…我会待他如己出{\r}\NAnd I'll... I'll make him one of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.78,0:04:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}给予他一切,一切!{\r}\NAnd give him everything. Everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.12,0:04:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}离太远了{\r}\N[Whispering] Far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.19,0:04:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}离太远,太远了{\r}\NSo far, far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.49,0:04:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但…但我需要她的协助{\r}\NBu-But I need her. I need her help.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.39,0:04:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我一个人做不到{\r}\NI can't do it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.06,0:04:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你看,我需要她的记忆{\r}\NYou see, I need her memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.10,0:04:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那都已经40年了 我不知道孩子被带到哪里…{\r}\NIt's over 40 years ago, and I don't know where the child was taken...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.74,0:04:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}或是送给了谁{\r}\Nor who it was given to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.74,0:04:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不知道他现在在哪里 或他现在是谁{\r}\NI don't know where he is now or who he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.31,0:04:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}对于衡量朱莉亚・兰伯特 真实的爱…{\r}\N[In Henry's Voice] The true measure of Julia Rainbird's love...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.58,0:04:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}在于她现在要如何去做{\r}\Nlies in what she does now,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.58,0:04:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}藉由你的帮助,当然,还有我的{\r}\Nwith your help, of course, and mine,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.18,0:04:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}亲爱的,离开吧…{\r}\Nand that of the dear, departed one...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.32,0:04:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是谁漂流远离了我们{\r}\Nwho has drifted so far from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.82,0:04:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们了解了,兰伯特女士,对吧?{\r}\N[In Normal Voice] We understand him. Don't we, Miss Rainbird?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.83,0:05:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}噢,是的,我是 我愿意去做任何事,任何的事{\r}\NOh, yes. Yes, I do. I'm willing to do anything. Anything at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.07,0:05:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}最后,幸福将会到来{\r}\N[In Henry's Voice] In the end, there will be happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.10,0:05:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}从逝去的眼泪当中 沙漠般的心灵会开出花朵{\r}\NFrom the tears of the past, the desert of the heart will bloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.68,0:05:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}再见,朱莉亚・兰伯特 再见,布兰琪{\r}\NGood-bye, Julia Rainbird! Good-bye, Blanche.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.88,0:05:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}再见{\r}\N[Softly] Good-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.42,0:05:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}布兰琪夫人,你没事吧?{\r}\N[Moans] Madame Blanche! Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.33,0:05:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}噢,这是…{\r}\NOh. It was... [Clears Throat, Noisily]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.80,0:05:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这到底是怎么回事?{\r}\NWhat in the world's been going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.80,0:05:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我觉得我好像做了什么事{\r}\NI feel as though I've been properly done over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.13,0:05:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你不记得发生什么了?{\r}\NDon't you remember what happened? Mm-mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.51,0:05:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不记得细节了,布兰琪女士 只有大略,你应该知道我的意思{\r}\NNot the details, Miss Rainbird, only the gist, if you know what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.74,0:05:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我以为你会告诉我一些要点{\r}\NSuppose you give me the gist of it. [Blows Nose]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.21,0:05:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}喔,我不知道…{\r}\NOh well, I wonder... [Gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.58,0:05:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我能麻烦你弄点什么喝的…{\r}\NCould I trouble you for a sip of something? Ju-Just...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.92,0:05:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}噢,当然,你要喝什么?{\r}\NOh, of course. What would you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.92,0:06:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}噢,随便给我一点混合的…{\r}\NOh, a double shot of anyth...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.19,0:06:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 来点雪莉酒或许比较好 - 噢,是的,没问题{\r}\N- A spot of that sherry might be nice. - Oh, yes. Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.53,0:06:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}谢谢{\r}\N[Sniffles] Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.90,0:06:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 现在,请告诉我还记得的招魂内容 - 说个大概?{\r}\N- Now, tell me what you remember of the seance. - In a nutshell?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.78,0:06:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}拜托了{\r}\NPlease.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.81,0:06:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}嗯…{\r}\NWell... [Clears Throat]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.12,0:06:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}大约40年前,你安排…{\r}\NAbout 40 years ago, you arranged to have...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.25,0:06:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}把你妹妹的小婴儿送给了别人{\r}\Nyour sister Harriet's baby given away without a trace.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.86,0:06:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如今你总是做噩梦 你困惑的良心告诉你{\r}\NAnd now your bad dreams and troubled conscience tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.02,0:06:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}必须去找到长大了的小孩 并带他回家{\r}\Nto find the grown-up person, take him into the family...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.73,0:06:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}给予他财富{\r}\Nand bestow your wealth on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.73,0:06:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 很好 - 谢谢{\r}\NExcellent. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.40,0:06:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但我为什么 要强迫我妹妹把小孩送人?{\r}\NAnd why did I force my sister to give the child away?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.07,0:06:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我想,那个小孩可能是…私生子 兰伯特女士{\r}\NI guess the kid was a... illegitimate, Miss Rainbird.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.14,0:06:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不希望你以为我是个清教徒 布兰琪夫人{\r}\NI don't want you to think me a puritan, Madame Blanche.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.18,0:07:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但是,40年前,未婚母亲{\r}\NBut 40 years ago, an unmarried mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.98,0:07:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}并不像现在这么普遍{\r}\Nwas not the commonplace it is nowadays.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.58,0:07:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}尤其是在我们这样的家族{\r}\NAnd in a family like ours,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.62,0:07:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不得不牺牲一切代价来掩盖丑闻{\r}\Na scandal had to be covered up at all costs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.56,0:07:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我明白{\r}\NI understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.86,0:07:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我必须保持传统{\r}\NAnd I'm still sufficiently old-fashioned,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.96,0:07:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}并维护兰伯特家的名声{\r}\Nand sufficiently protective of the Rainbird name,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.96,0:07:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}寻找失踪的继承人时…{\r}\Nto want to seek the missing heir...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.97,0:07:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}必须以私人并秘密的方式进行{\r}\Nin a private and secret fashion,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.14,0:07:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}而不是去找侦探社{\r}\Nrather than go to detective agencies...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.17,0:07:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}或是登报寻人{\r}\Nand put notices in the newspapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.31,0:07:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这是个明智的决定 兰伯特女士{\r}\NA most wise decision, Miss Rainbird.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.18,0:07:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那么,现在 我们找到了必须请你帮忙的理由{\r}\NWell, now, suppose we get to the reason...\Nfor my sending for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.62,0:07:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我已经78岁了{\r}\NI'm 78 years of age.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.29,0:07:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我希望能带着一颗平静的心 跨进棺材{\r}\NI would like to go to my grave with a quiet conscience.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.72,0:07:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}特别是当我知道唯一的继承人 就在外面的某个地方{\r}\NParticularly as I know that my only heir is out there somewhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.26,0:07:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是我的行为 剥夺了他兰伯特的姓氏{\r}\Ndeprived by my acts of his true Rainbird name.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.30,0:07:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你能用你的力量帮助我吗?{\r}\NWill you help me with your powers?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.54,0:07:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如果你是诚心的,我可以{\r}\NIf in your heart you believe that I can,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.94,0:08:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我有责任让我们共同去尝试 兰伯特女士{\r}\Nthen I owe it to both of us to try, Miss Rainbird.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.88,0:08:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不,我太老了,做不到了{\r}\NNo, I'm too old for trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.95,0:08:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我只来得及去看到结果{\r}\NI've only time enough left for results!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.01,0:08:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}帮我找到他,布兰琪夫人 用你的精神力量,还有你的亨利{\r}\NFind him for me, Madame Blanche. Use your spirit-control, your "Henry."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.62,0:08:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}透过我的妹妹{\r}\NGet through to my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.86,0:08:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}找到她的儿子 查出他是谁,无论他的身分{\r}\NFind her son, whoever he is, wherever he is,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.99,0:08:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我会付给你一万美元{\r}\Nand I'll pay you $10,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.50,0:08:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}一万…{\r}\NTe...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.54,0:08:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如果你是真心的,兰伯特女士{\r}\NOnly if you genuinely wish to, Miss Rainbird.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.17,0:08:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但是不要认为这些钱是付给了我{\r}\NBut let's not think of this as a payment to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.24,0:08:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}因为我很有爱心{\r}\NThere are many causes dear to my heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.68,0:08:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}世上所有的慈善机构都需要它{\r}\Nwhich need all the charity the world can spare.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.15,0:08:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你不知道它让一个女人多么振奋 我的财富{\r}\NYou've no idea how refreshing it is for a woman of my wealth...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.45,0:08:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}找个人只需要用到这么一点点钱{\r}\Nto find someone who has so little use for money.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.32,0:08:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}谢谢{\r}\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.42,0:08:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那么,我想我们已经谈妥了{\r}\N[Sighs] Well, now, I regard our arrangement as completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.20,0:08:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我的睡觉时间到了{\r}\NI... It's my bedtime.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.17,0:09:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我必须向你这位 令人愉快的客人告别了{\r}\NI must take leave of your delightful company.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.84,0:09:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}对我来说这是一个难忘的夜晚 兰伯特女士{\r}\NThis has been a most memorable evening for me, Miss Rainbird.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.87,0:09:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你让钱发挥了更大的价值{\r}\NSee to it that you make it a rewarding one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.84,0:09:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你让自己反覆的陷入险境{\r}\NAt the risk of repeating myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.51,0:09:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我希望你不要忘记…{\r}\NI hope you will not forget...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.51,0:09:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}没有人,绝对没有任何人 能知道我们的寻找行动{\r}\Nthat nobody, absolutely no one,\Nshould know of our search.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.02,0:09:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}兰伯特家的名声必须受到保护{\r}\NThe Rainbird name must be protected.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.29,0:09:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我保证守口如瓶{\r}\NMy jaw is locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.62,0:09:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}一言为定,再见了 感谢你的光临{\r}\NOn that note, I will say good-bye, and thank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.33,0:10:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}事情怎么样了?{\r}\NSo, how'd it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.93,0:10:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不知道,扮演亨利 简直是在谋杀我的喉咙{\r}\NI don't know. Having to do Henry is murder on my throat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.27,0:10:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 谋杀 - 是,是,我明白{\r}\N- Murder. - Yeah, yeah. I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.27,0:10:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 那事情怎么样了? - 她上钩了,就等着被拉上来{\r}\N- So how did it go? - She's hooked, waiting to be pulled in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.61,0:10:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}另一条价值25元的沙丁鱼?{\r}\NAnother one of your $25 sardines?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.45,0:10:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不,这是条大鱼,乔治 一条大鲸鱼{\r}\NNo. This is a big one, George. A great big whale.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.58,0:10:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}哦,快点,告诉我{\r}\NWell, come on. Give.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.82,0:10:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}把你的眼睛留在路上,别催我{\r}\NKeep your eyes on the road. Don't rush me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.92,0:10:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好的,布兰琪{\r}\N[Sighs] Okay, Blanchie.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.49,0:10:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}洗耳恭听{\r}\NStart way up at the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.93,0:10:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}嗯,就像收听ABC广播一样简单 亨利来找我,来自天上{\r}\NWell, it was as simple as A-B-C. Henry came to me from the Upper Brightness,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.96,0:10:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}低声对我说 "这位女士长期有睡眠的困扰"{\r}\Nwhispered to me, "This womars been having sleep problems."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.50,0:10:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}之后就顺其自然,按照逻辑{\r}\NFrom there on, things followed naturally, logically.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.17,0:10:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}啊哈,我一次又帮了你大忙啊 亲爱的?{\r}\NAha! So I came through for you again, didn't I, darlin?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.47,0:10:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不,你在说什么,乔治?{\r}\NNo. What are you talking about, George?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.74,0:10:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你是什么意思,我说了什么?{\r}\NWhat do you mean, what am I talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.94,0:10:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你他妈的知道我在说什么{\r}\NYou know damn well what I'm talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.85,0:10:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}所有的资讯 是我向当地的药剂师挖来的…{\r}\NAll that information that I dug up by gabbir to the local druggist...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.62,0:10:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}关于她被失眠搞得快发疯…{\r}\Nabout how she was drivir him crazy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.62,0:10:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}试图没有处方购买安眠药{\r}\Ntryir to get sleeping pills without a prescription!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.62,0:11:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这本来对我非常非常有用{\r}\NThat could have been very, very useful to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.16,0:11:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}为什么你没告诉我这些事?{\r}\NWhy didn't you tell me about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.16,0:11:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你什么意思? 我没告诉你? 你他妈的知道我告诉过你{\r}\NWhat do you mean, why didn't I tell you? I told you. You know damn well I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.93,0:11:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不,你总是以为你告诉过我事情 但其实你忘了{\r}\NNo, you always think you tell me things, and you forget to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.70,0:11:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我必须跨越天堂与地狱 去和亨利沟通{\r}\NI have to go through heaven and hell, the Great Beyond, with Henry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.90,0:11:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}亨利,听好,是我{\r}\NHenry, my ass. It was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.24,0:11:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}总是我{\r}\NIt's always me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.51,0:11:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如果没有我的调查 你这通灵人不过是个干腊肠{\r}\NWithout my research, you're about as psychic as a dry salami.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.81,0:11:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}龌龊,龌龊,龌龊{\r}\N[Sighs] Nasty. Nasty, nasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.35,0:11:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我已经厌烦了当你的水晶球{\r}\NI'm sick and tired of having you hang me by the crystal balls.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.22,0:11:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}顾好你自己的水晶球吧,乔治{\r}\NLeave your crystal balls out of this, George.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.19,0:11:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不,别谈亨利了 把废话留给你的客户吧{\r}\NNo, let's leave Henry out of this and keep the bullshit for your customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.79,0:11:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你嫉妒他,是吗?{\r}\NYou're jealous of him, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.86,0:11:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}喔,拜托,布兰琪{\r}\NOh, please, Blanche.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.90,0:11:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我喜欢你的嫉妒 这是你这驾驶的臭味{\r}\NI like your jealousy. It's your driving that stinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.37,0:11:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}嘿,听着,我偶尔也是个演员 不是计程车司机{\r}\NHey, look. I happen to be an actor, not a cab driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.57,0:11:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我当然能扮演司机 但我相信地狱不需要一位驾驶{\r}\NI can play cab drivers, but I sure as hell don't have to drive like one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.84,0:11:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}哦,直到我赚到 朱莉亚・兰伯特这一票以前{\r}\NWell, until I can collect from Julia Rainbird,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.18,0:11:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}恐怕你需要 继续扮演好计程车司机{\r}\NI'm afraid you're gonna have to go on playing a cab driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.88,0:11:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们俩都不希望饿死{\r}\NNeither of us seems to be very fond of starving to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.98,0:12:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}哦,我们该如何干这票 这条兰伯特鲸鱼能喷出多少钱?{\r}\NWell, how are we supposed to collect? How much is this Rainbird whale gonna spout up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.65,0:12:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你要继续扮演好私家侦探{\r}\NAlso, you're gonna have to go on playing a private eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.82,0:12:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}上帝,不! 我已经演够了私家侦探{\r}\NChrist, no! I've had it playing private eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.32,0:12:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}上帝,是的! 乔治{\r}\NChrist, yes! Now, George.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.86,0:12:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}停止亵渎吧{\r}\NStop blaspheming.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.10,0:12:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你想要诅咒十张大钞?{\r}\NYou wanna put the curse on ten big ones?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.90,0:12:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}等一等,布兰琪{\r}\NNow, wait a minute, Blanche.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.24,0:12:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你说十张大钞? - 嗯哼{\r}\N- Did you say ten big ones? - Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.07,0:12:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 一万? - 嗯哼{\r}\N- Ten thousand? - Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.07,0:12:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 美元? - 美元,乔治!{\r}\N- Dollars? - Dollars, George!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.68,0:12:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}现在,布兰琪,你想想…{\r}\N[Chuckles] Now, Blanche, you got any idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.21,0:12:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们能如何花这一万美元?{\r}\Nwhat you and I could do with ten grand?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.22,0:12:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}嗯哼,我们甚至可以结婚{\r}\NMm-hmm. We could even get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.35,0:12:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}为什么你总是要扫兴呢?{\r}\NWhat are you always a wet blanket for?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.29,0:12:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}哈,你太夸奖我了{\r}\N[Laughs] Oh, you flatter me so.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.89,0:12:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那么,怎么做? 我们该做什么?{\r}\NWell, what's the deal? What do we have to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.89,0:12:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我晚点会在床上告诉你的{\r}\NI'll tell you about it in bed, afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.26,0:12:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}噢,拜托,布兰琪,给我一点暗示{\r}\NAw, come on, Blanche. Give me a hint.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.87,0:12:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}只是一点…前戏{\r}\NJust a little... [Chuckles] Fore play.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.70,0:12:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好吧,找一个人,就这样{\r}\NAll right. Find one man. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.70,0:12:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}哦,我们做过更糟糕的事 他叫什么名字?{\r}\NWell, we've had to do worse than that. What's his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.81,0:13:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}呃…没有人知道{\r}\NHmm. Ah... nobody knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.28,0:13:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 那么,他是谁? - 好问题,没有人知道{\r}\N- Well, who is he? - That's a problem. Nobody knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.72,0:13:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 他在哪里? - 没有人知道{\r}\N- [Laughs] Where is he? - Nobody knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.49,0:13:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}喔,别说笑了,你的意思是 都没有人知道,布兰琪?{\r}\NWell, for chrissake! You mean, nobody knows, Blanche?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.29,0:13:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}没有人知道他的名字 他在哪里,或者他是谁?{\r}\NNobody knows his name, or where he is, or who he is?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.72,0:13:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}嘿,乔治,别叫了{\r}\NWell, George, stop yelling.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.86,0:13:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}有个人可能会知道{\r}\NThere's a possibility of one person who might have known.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.70,0:13:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 哦,是谁? - 朱莉亚・兰伯特没有对我提到他{\r}\N- Well, who's that? - Julia Rainbird didn't mention him to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.00,0:13:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}幸运的是 她的朋友爱达・库克森跟我说了{\r}\NFortunately, her friend Ida Cookson did.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.60,0:13:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 哦,那是谁? - 兰伯特的私人司机{\r}\N- Well, who is it? - The Rainbird family chauffeur.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.44,0:13:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}哦,你总算说出了一条正道{\r}\N[Sighs] Well, now you're talkir. Now we're on our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.78,0:13:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}麻烦的是…呃…{\r}\NTrouble is... Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.71,0:13:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他已经死了25年{\r}\Nhe's been dead for 25 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.82,0:13:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}喔,别再说笑了,布兰琪…{\r}\NOh, for chrissake, Blanche...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.12,0:13:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}喔,不不不,别紧张,乔治{\r}\NOh, no, no, no, no, no, don't start to fret, George,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.65,0:13:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}否则今晚我们在水床上 将会失去乐趣{\r}\Nor our water bed will be no fun at all tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.02,0:13:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}做为一个演员,你应该知道 烦躁会毁了演出的{\r}\NAs an actor, you should know fretting will ruin a performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.26,0:13:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你该不会是在担心 我今晚的表现吧{\r}\NYou're not gonna have to worry about my performance tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.93,0:13:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}事实上,今天晚上{\r}\NAs a matter of fact, uh, on this very evening,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.16,0:14:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你会想要起立鼓掌的{\r}\Nyou're gonna see a standing ovation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.11,0:14:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}她在这里,不,不是男的 是个女人{\r}\NShe's here. No, not a man. It's a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.72,0:14:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好的,跟我来{\r}\NRight. Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.21,0:15:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}只要维克多・康斯坦丁 还在你手上,我们就不能动你{\r}\NAs long as you've got Victor Constantine, we can't touch you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.11,0:15:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}所以,你不如把那东西放下吧{\r}\NSo you might as well put that thing away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.26,0:15:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你一直称自己为"交易人" 因此我们以为你是一个男人{\r}\N[Man #1] You've been calling yourself"The Trader," so we thought you were a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.78,0:15:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我认为我们也应该得到一些保证 确认肉票仍然活着{\r}\N[Man #2] I think we deserve some assurance that the victim is still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.22,0:16:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}按照你的指示 无线电已经从直升机上移除{\r}\N[Man #1] All radios have been removed from the helicopter, as you instructed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.96,0:16:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}"康斯坦丁先生正在昏睡当中 只要等安眠药药效退去就会醒来"{\r}\N"Mr. Constantine will be unconscious but in perfect condition when picked up.\NJust let him sleep the drug off."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.57,0:16:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好吧,警长,开灯{\r}\NAll right, Sergeant, turn on the lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.77,0:16:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 别逞英雄 - 是的,先生{\r}\N- Don't try and be a hero. - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.78,0:16:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好,我们已经尽了我们的部分{\r}\NWell, we've done our part.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.25,0:17:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们要去哪?{\r}\NWhere are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.21,0:17:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}别发生任何该死的错误{\r}\NNot one goddamn mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.35,0:17:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}还要飞多远?{\r}\NHow far are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.66,0:17:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你运气真好 他们还愿意为肉票付出{\r}\NIt's lucky for you they've still got the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.02,0:17:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}更重要的是我把你扔下去 这件事没发生在你身上{\r}\NI'd like nothing better than to toss you right out of this thing on your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.07,0:17:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}当然,这趟小旅行是你预订的 不是吗?{\r}\NYou sure have this little trip mapped out, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.41,0:18:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我打赌,那东西甚至没装子弹{\r}\NI bet that thing isn't even loaded.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.03,0:18:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}高尔夫球场?{\r}\NGolf course, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.33,0:19:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}耀眼,非常完美{\r}\NBrilliant. Absolutely perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.93,0:20:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我的脚快断了 这该死的六英几吒鞋{\r}\NMy feet are killing me. These damn six-inch heels.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.56,0:20:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我恰巧喜欢高挑的女人{\r}\NI happen to like tall women.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.13,0:20:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}每个人都喜欢高挑的女人{\r}\NEverybody likes tall women.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.94,0:20:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}事实上,每个人都在寻找 高挑的女人{\r}\NIn fact, everyone's going to be looking for a tall woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.87,0:20:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但总是不尽如人意{\r}\NAside from complaining a lot,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.87,0:20:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你最近都在做些什么?{\r}\Nwhat have you been doing with yourself lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.01,0:20:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}噢,没什么,抱赎金啦 诸如此类的事情{\r}\NOh, nothing much. Picking up a ransom, that sort of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.15,0:20:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你有看到任何 我们不知道的人吗?{\r}\NDid you see anyone, uh, we know?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.88,0:20:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}有两个看来是警察 另外第三个绝对是FBI{\r}\NTwo men who look like police and a third who just had to be F.B.I.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.55,0:20:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}最常和你打交道的人{\r}\NYou mix with the nicest people.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.22,0:20:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}家常便饭{\r}\NBeats housework.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.36,0:20:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你有对他们说什么? - 一个声音也没发出{\r}\N- Did you say anything to them? - Not a syllable.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.26,0:20:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你看吧,亲爱的{\r}\NNow, you see, honey?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.50,0:20:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我说过你可以学着缄默 只要你去尝试{\r}\NI told you you could learn to keep your mouth shut, if you tried.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.94,0:20:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}瞧瞧是谁在这里?{\r}\NLook who's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.58,0:20:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}嗯,有没有人看到一位身材高挑的 金发美女,刚才她还在这里{\r}\NMm. Has anyone seen a tall, blonde woman around here lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.95,0:20:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}喔,走掉了,有谁会需要她?{\r}\NGone, poof! Who needs her?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.95,0:21:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我要,至少多留点时间给我吧{\r}\NI do. At least one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.94,0:22:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好了,亲爱的{\r}\NLet me put that there, darlin.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.64,0:22:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}康斯坦丁先生给我们 留了一点葡萄酒{\r}\NMr. Constantine has left us some wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.01,0:22:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不认为他喜欢进口的东西{\r}\NI don't think he likes the imported stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.75,0:22:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}嗯…还有我的牛肉干酪{\r}\NUh... It was probably my veal parmesan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.82,0:22:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我想我煮得太烂了 - 他喜欢在餐厅吃东西,就这样{\r}\N- I'm afraid I overcooked it. - He likes eating in a room with a view, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.32,0:22:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你知道,有钱人很挑剔的{\r}\NYou know how fussy rich people are.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.49,0:22:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}别忘了洗干净{\r}\NDon't forget to empty that out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.16,0:22:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你不觉得洗马桶 有损宝石收藏家的尊严吗?{\r}\NDon't you think emptying a chemical toilet...\Nis below the dignity of a jewel collector?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.46,0:22:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 真是罪恶的工作啊,亚瑟 - 我明天再做{\r}\N- The wages of sin, Arthur. - I'll do it tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.24,0:22:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不能拖到明天…{\r}\NNever put off till tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.47,0:23:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 或是你今晚也可以先略过 - 婊子{\r}\N- what you can empty out tonight. - Bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.71,0:23:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}亚瑟,阿姆斯特丹是怎样的地方?{\r}\NArthur, what's Amsterdam like?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.44,0:23:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}喔,大量的运河{\r}\NOh, lots of canals.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.45,0:23:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}很多干瘪的老头…{\r}\NLots of wizened old men...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.62,0:23:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}坐在大石头上 以锐利的目光盯着年轻人{\r}\Nwith sharp eyes, sitting around cutting big stones into little ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.25,0:23:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你会看到的{\r}\NYou'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.09,0:23:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不知道什么是影响我 今晚我浑身感到不舒服{\r}\NI don't know what's come over me tonight. I'm tingling all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.90,0:24:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我告诉过你危险的,不是吗?{\r}\NI told you about danger, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.87,0:24:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}首先,它使你生病{\r}\NFirst it makes you sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.37,0:24:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}当你平安度过,它又让你非常…{\r}\NThen, when you get through it, it makes you very,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.74,0:24:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}非常热爱{\r}\Nvery loving.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.88,0:24:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 亲爱的,这… - 嗯?{\r}\N- Darling, is it... - Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.15,0:24:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这太过容易了,让人害怕{\r}\NIt was all too easy. It's frightening.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.39,0:24:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}出色的计划{\r}\N[Sighs] Brilliant planning.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.99,0:24:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他们没有任何线索可以追踪{\r}\NThey don't have a single lead to follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.73,0:24:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们对他用的麻药有效吗?{\r}\NWhat about the ketamine we stuck him with?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.33,0:24:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}哦,如果沃格尔医生六个月前 拔我的臼齿时有效{\r}\NWell, if Doctor Vogel didn't miss it six months ago when I had my wisdom tooth out,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.07,0:24:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}现在对他一样有效吧{\r}\Nhe's not gonna miss it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.07,0:24:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不要在这里浪费时间了 我们上床吧{\r}\NDon't finish up in there. Let's go to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.44,0:24:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 累了吗? - 嗯,全身酸痛{\r}\N- Tired? - Mm-mm. Tingling all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.14,0:24:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}为什么我会让你占有这一切?{\r}\NHow'd I ever let you get me into all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.91,0:24:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我想我爱上了你 因为我需要一些稳定{\r}\NI thought I fell in love with you because I needed some stability.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.08,0:24:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}哦,我猜只是你的性格不好{\r}\NWell, I guess you're just a bad judge of character.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.02,0:24:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你把到手的钻石放在哪? - 大家都看得到的地方{\r}\N- Where'd you put the diamond, dear? - Where everyone can see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.55,0:24:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你才没有 - 我有{\r}\N- You didn't. - I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.82,0:25:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你要告诉我在哪里吗? - 你得先折磨我{\r}\N- Are you gonna tell me where? - You'll have to torture me first.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.46,0:25:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}喔,我正打算呢{\r}\NOh! [Giggling] I intend to.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.70,0:25:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}就在几分钟后{\r}\NIn a few minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.00,0:25:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我已经够尊重FBI和督察局了{\r}\NNow, with all due respect to the F.B.I. And the Bureau of Inspectors,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.11,0:25:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我没有时间玩游戏{\r}\NI have no time to play games.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.44,0:25:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不要忘记,先生们 我已经强烈的想离开这个办公桌{\r}\NNow, lest we forget, gentlemen, I have been away from this desk forcibly.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.31,0:25:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我还有许多工作赶着做{\r}\NI've got a lot of work to catch up on.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.31,0:25:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这该死的事情 我们还要谈多少回?{\r}\NNow, how many more times we gonna go through this goddamn thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.12,0:25:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}直到我们找到线索为止 康斯坦丁先生{\r}\NUntil we come up with something, Mr. Constantine.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.66,0:25:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这种解决绑架的方法真是地狱{\r}\NThat's a hell of a way to solve a kidnapping.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.82,0:25:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}康斯坦丁先生,你要知道 你不是第一个受害者,还有其他人{\r}\NMr. Constantine, you're not the first victim, you know. There have been others.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.33,0:25:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好了,好了,但是从我这里 你们也得不到线索的{\r}\NAll right, all right. But from me, you'll learn absolutely nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.20,0:25:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你永远不会知道 - 我知道{\r}\N- You never know. - I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.70,0:25:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好吧,弗伊{\r}\NAll right. Floyd?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.90,0:25:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}现在,从地下停车场说起{\r}\NNow. The underground garage.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.37,0:25:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 停满了车 - 声音呢?{\r}\N- Full of cars. - Sounds?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.14,0:25:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 有个人在我身后 - 是男人还是女人?{\r}\N- People, behind me. - Was it a man, or was it a woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.38,0:25:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我不知道 - 男人还是女人?{\r}\N- I don't know. - Man or woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.38,0:25:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 男人 - 然后呢?{\r}\N- Man. - Then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.71,0:25:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}就在我正要转身时 我的肩膀一阵刺痛{\r}\N[Grunts] It was a prick in my shoulder. I started to turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.79,0:26:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}接着,我在一个房间里醒来{\r}\NEh...And I woke up in a room.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.35,0:26:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是的,你有听到什么吗? 屋内或屋外的声音?{\r}\N[Floyd] Yes, and what did you hear? Inside or outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.86,0:26:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}房间是隔音的{\r}\NThe room was soundproofed.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.16,0:26:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我什么都听不到 除了扬声器里传来空洞的声音{\r}\NI never heard anything except a disembodied voice of a loudspeaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.93,0:26:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 描述一下 - 但我已经说过了{\r}\N- Describe it. - But I've already done that.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.84,0:26:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}再说一次!{\r}\NAgain!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.20,0:26:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是一个男人的声音,没有口音{\r}\NIt was the voice of a man, no accent.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.91,0:26:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 电子变声过,无法辨识 - 有几个人在那里?{\r}\N- Doctored up electronically. Unrecognizable. - How many of them were there?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.35,0:26:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}两个,一男一女{\r}\NTwo. A man and a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.85,0:26:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你为什么这么说? - 因为只有微弱的光线照射下来{\r}\N- Why do you say that? - Because the faintest light filtered down from above.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.15,0:26:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不足以给我机会看看他们是谁{\r}\NBut not enough to give me a chance to see who they were.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.76,0:26:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 那么是谁煮饭? - 她煮的{\r}\N- Yes, and who did the cooking? - She did.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.99,0:26:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 为什么? - 因为男人不会费心思…{\r}\N- Why? - Because a man would not bother to put the parsley...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.73,0:26:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}在鱼排上放香芹,这就是原因{\r}\Non the filet of sole, that's why.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.73,0:26:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 她多大年纪? - 喔,拜托{\r}\N- How old is she? - Come on, now. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.17,0:26:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 她多大年纪? - 25{\r}\N- How old is she? - Twenty-five.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.14,0:26:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 为什么? - 为什么?{\r}\N- Why? - Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.31,0:26:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如果像我这样年龄的男人 要被一个女人绑架{\r}\NBecause if a man my age is gonna get kidnapped by a woman,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.81,0:26:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他希望她有25岁,这就是原因{\r}\Nhe wants her to be 25, that's why.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.18,0:27:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 描述一下你如何被释放 - 释放…{\r}\N- Describe your return. - The return.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.48,0:27:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那空洞的声音叫我坐下来 并背对着门{\r}\NThe disembodied voice tells me to sit with my back to the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.65,0:27:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}灯光熄灭,门打开,他们走了进来{\r}\NThe light goes out, the door opens, they both come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.02,0:27:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我感到左手臂一阵刺痛{\r}\NI feel a prick in my left arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.93,0:27:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}接下来我只知道 我在医院的病床上醒来{\r}\NThe next thing I know, I wake up in that hospital bed...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.13,0:27:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你就坐在那里,开始问东问西的{\r}\Nwith you sitting there, thinking up questions!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.63,0:27:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}谢谢,康斯坦丁先生 你做得很好{\r}\NThank you, Mr. Constantine. You're doing great.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.24,0:27:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 这就是你的感想 - 好,让我们重头开始{\r}\N- That's what you think. - All right, let's start all over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.61,0:27:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}噢,妈的!{\r}\NAw, shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.44,0:28:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}亨利,为什么你面带微笑?{\r}\N[Blanche] Why, Henry, you have such a beaming smile on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.64,0:28:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我微笑是因为我很高兴,布兰琪{\r}\N[Blanche Playing Henry] I smile because I'm happy, Blanche.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.98,0:28:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}能透过你,布兰琪 传达讯息给你朋友,爱达・库克森{\r}\NIt comes through you, Blanche, from your friend, Ida Cookson.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.68,0:28:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我是她的向导,亨利{\r}\N[In Blanche's Voice] I'm her guide, Henry.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.45,0:28:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}只有在不被否认的时候 才能称为真正的友谊{\r}\NFriendship can be claimed only when it cannot be denied.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.12,0:28:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}告诉爱达・库克森 我们在这里都很感谢…{\r}\N[In Henry's Voice] Tell Ida Cookson we're all thankful here...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.12,0:28:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}她温暖而宁静的心灵{\r}\Nfor the warm tranquility in her heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.63,0:28:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}因为她信任你,使得这更加温暖{\r}\NIt will grow even warmer as she trusts in you,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.53,0:28:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}向你倾诉,没有对你保留秘密…{\r}\Nand confides in you, and holds back no secrets from you...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.47,0:28:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}无论是对她自己 或是她的亲密朋友{\r}\Nbe they her own, or those of her intimate friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.24,0:28:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你听到了吗? 库克森夫人{\r}\N[Blanche's Voice] Did you hear that, Mrs. Cookson?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.97,0:28:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是的,布兰琪夫人{\r}\N[Mrs. Cookson] Yes, Madame Blanche.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.98,0:28:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}亨利,我需要你 帮我们寻找沃尔特{\r}\N[Blanche] Henry, I want you to seek Walter for us now.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.68,0:28:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}透过善意的寻找,直到…{\r}\NSearch through to the Double Strand of Kindness, until...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.75,0:28:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我的朋友爱达・库克森 能加入这爱的交流{\r}\Nmy friend Ida Cookson is joined in loving communication...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.22,0:28:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}与她亲爱的丈夫沟通{\r}\Nwith her dear, departed husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.43,0:28:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我试试看,布兰琪{\r}\N[In Henry's Voice] I will try, Blanche.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.73,0:29:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但是首先,必须让迷雾消散 并揭起薄纱{\r}\NBut first, the mist must part a little, and the veil must rise...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.07,0:29:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}让光线指引我们道路{\r}\Nto let in the light that will show us the path.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.24,0:29:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我准备好了,亨利{\r}\N[In Blanche's Voice] Ah, I'm ready now, Henry.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.61,0:29:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}准备,准备好了跟随你 无论你要我去哪儿{\r}\NReady! Ready to follow you, wherever you want me to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.18,0:29:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}哪里? 你要带我到哪里,亨利?{\r}\NWhere? Where are you taking me, Henry?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.28,0:29:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是的,是的,我看到了{\r}\N[Gasps] Yes, yes, yes! I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.58,0:29:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我看到你在向我招手{\r}\NI see your hand beckoning to me. [Laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.19,0:29:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}喔,多么迷人的花园啊,亨利{\r}\NOh, what a lovely garden, Henry.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.66,0:29:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我…我,喔!{\r}\NMy, my. Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.43,0:29:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那是…那是一尊雕像吗?{\r}\NIs that... Is that a statue there?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.40,0:29:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}噢,那是沃尔特站在喷泉旁边吗?{\r}\NOh! Could this be Walter standing beside the fountain?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.90,0:29:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你怎么能这样对我? - 我需要你的车钥匙…{\r}\N[Whispering] - How can you do this to me? - I need your car keys.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.91,0:29:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我赶时间 - 喔!{\r}\N- I'm in a hurry. - Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.91,0:29:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你知道打断我的思绪 会造成什么损害吗?{\r}\NDo you realize what damage you can do my psyche, breaking in this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.11,0:29:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}只要给我你的钥匙,我赶时间{\r}\NJust give me your keys. I need 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.31,0:29:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是的,亨利! 要干嘛?{\r}\N[Shouting] Yes, Henry! [Whispering] What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.31,0:29:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我找到兰伯特司机的女儿了{\r}\NI've located the daughter of the Rainbird chauffeur.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.32,0:29:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我这计程车司机却去不了 - 喔!{\r}\N- And I'm not going as a cab driver. - [Shouting] Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.72,0:29:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你说我应该做的,我却没有车? - 我才不在乎你做什么{\r}\N- What am I supposed to do without my car? - I don't care what you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.29,0:29:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我开计程车,只要给我钥匙 - 树在摇动!{\r}\N- Take a taxi. Just give me the keys. - The trees are swaying!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.69,0:30:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}枝叶分开了!{\r}\NAnd the branches part!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.16,0:30:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但那儿一个人也没有! 在这里{\r}\NBut there's no one there! [Whispering] Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.76,0:30:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我看到影子消失了! 空气越来越冷!{\r}\NI see shadows falling! The air is getting cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.40,0:30:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}光线变暗了,再见,亨利!{\r}\NThe brightness... dims. Good-bye, Henry!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.30,0:30:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}喔!{\r}\NOh! [Chimes Tinkling]
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.27,0:30:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你找到沃尔特了?{\r}\N[Gasps] Did you find Walter?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.24,0:30:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 在哪里? - 在厨房里啊{\r}\N- Where? - In the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.28,0:30:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}没错{\r}\NI did.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.50,0:30:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不知道能不能和你谈几分钟 海妮根女士?{\r}\NI wonder if I could speak to you for a couple minutes, Mrs. Hannagan.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.00,0:30:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}当然,我们认识吗?{\r}\NWhy, sure. Do we know each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.77,0:30:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不,我叫法兰克・麦克布莱 弗格森和麦克布莱律师事务所的{\r}\NNo, I'm Frank McBride, of the law firm of Ferguson, Ferguson & McBride,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.91,0:30:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我只是想知道,如果你不介意 回答一些关于你背景的问题{\r}\Nand I just wondered if you would mind...\Nanswering a couple questions about your background.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.68,0:30:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我的背景? - 嗯{\r}\NMy background? Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.68,0:30:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}就像洗碗水一样无趣{\r}\N[Chuckles] Dull as dishwater.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.68,0:30:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我的意思是 你为什么会想知道这个?{\r}\NI mean, what in the world would you be wanting with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.48,0:30:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}呃,这样说吧,嗯…{\r}\NWell, let's just say that the, uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.95,0:31:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我对那些讯息感兴趣 是因为值不少钱{\r}\Ninformation that I'm interested in could be won'th a great deal of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.66,0:31:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}哦,是吗? 给谁?{\r}\N- Oh, yeah? To who? - Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.89,0:31:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}嗯,我们只要花一点点时间 问几个愉快的小问题,如果你不介意{\r}\NWell, we'll get around to that pleasant little subject in a minute, if you don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.83,0:31:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 好吧 - 太好了{\r}\N- Okay. - Oh, swell.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.87,0:31:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}现在,我们从头开始吧?{\r}\NNow, why don't we just start at the beginning?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.80,0:31:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你的父母呢? - 喔,他们都过世了,蒙主宠召{\r}\N- Your parents. - Oh, they're both dead. God rest 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.07,0:31:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你的父亲是一名司机,对吧? - 你怎么知道?{\r}\NYour father was a chauffeur, though, right? How did you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.71,0:31:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他是兰伯特家族的司机{\r}\N[Chuckles] He was a chauffeur for the Rainbird family.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.48,0:31:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}又说对了! 你像是个冥界的侦探 麦克布莱先生{\r}\NRight again! You'd be a hell of a detective, Mr. McBride.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.42,0:31:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这我可就不知道了,亲爱的{\r}\N[Chuckles] I don't know about that, my dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.92,0:31:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这段时间,你还记不记得有谁…{\r}\NNow, during this period of time, though, can you remember anybody, uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.99,0:31:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是你父亲的亲密朋友?{\r}\Nbeing a close friend of your father's?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.39,0:31:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}嗯,是有一个人 很久以前了,当时我还在读书{\r}\NUh, there was a man. It was away back when I was in school.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.70,0:31:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那人经常和我父亲一起喝啤酒{\r}\NUh, there was this guy that my father used to drink beer with...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.17,0:31:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}并一起到村里打撞球{\r}\Nand shoot pool with down in the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.60,0:31:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这哈利・休奎奇 和他太太莎蒂开了一间家禽店{\r}\NThis Harry Shoebridge had a poultry shop with his wife, Sadie.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.37,0:31:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}休奎奇{\r}\N[Chuckles] Shoebridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.38,0:31:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是啊,他的生意一直很差{\r}\NYeah. His business was always lousy,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.38,0:32:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}即使在景气好的时候{\r}\Neven when times were good.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.31,0:32:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}她曾经流产过…{\r}\NAnd she used to have miscarriages...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.35,0:32:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}就像其他女人一样不再过生日{\r}\Nlike other women have birthdays.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.85,0:32:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}后来,他们放弃并搬走了{\r}\NWell, they stopped trying, and they moved away...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.82,0:32:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}搬到巴洛溪去 并收养了一个小孩,我想{\r}\Nto Barlow Creek, and, uh, adopted a kid, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.43,0:32:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 男孩吗? - 是啊,一个婴儿{\r}\NA boy? Yeah. An infant.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.73,0:32:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但是,你知道的,我不太确定{\r}\NBut, you know, I'm not so sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.70,0:32:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我…记忆有些模糊,嗯…{\r}\NI... It's all kind of hazy, an-and, uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.73,0:32:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我试着回想…{\r}\NI keep connecting it with...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.40,0:32:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}嗯,我记得有一晚{\r}\N[Bell Dinging] Well, I remember this night...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.31,0:32:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我父亲从休奎奇那里 一个人开车回家{\r}\Nwith my Dad driving over there...\Nto the Shoebridge's all alone, and then getting in...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.18,0:32:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}然后和我妈妈大吵了一架 因为他回到家时已经凌晨四点了{\r}\Na big fight with Ma because he'd come home at 4:00 A.M.,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.45,0:32:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}且他不告诉她 他到底去做了些什么{\r}\Nand he wouldn't tell her what he was doing or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.79,0:32:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}现在,我父亲过世了 愿上帝保佑他的灵魂安息{\r}\NNow, after my dad passed away... God rest his soul...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.02,0:32:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我妈妈非常痛恨休奎奇{\r}\Nmy ma was damn mad at the Shoebridge's,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.83,0:32:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}因为他们一直没有来参加葬礼{\r}\Nbecause they never showed up at the funeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.36,0:32:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 后来,她发现了原因 - 为什么?{\r}\N- Then she found out why. - Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.33,0:32:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}就在一年前 他们参加了自己的葬礼{\r}\NA year earlier, they'd gone to their own funeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.30,0:32:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 死了? - 嗯{\r}\N- Dead? - Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.97,0:33:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 他们和房子一起烧死了 - 那么,小孩怎么了?{\r}\N- Their house burned down with them in it. - Well, what about the son?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.74,0:33:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}海妮根女士! 你没看到有顾客吗?{\r}\NMrs. Hannagan! Can't you see that there are customers?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.38,0:33:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 噢,好的,我马上过去 - 她马上过去,夫人{\r}\N- Oh, yes. Yes. I'll be right there. - She'll be right there, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.12,0:33:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}嗯,听着,麦克布莱先生{\r}\NUh-Uh, look, um, Mr. McBride,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.89,0:33:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 事情差不多就这样了 - 海妮根女士{\r}\N- about all this being won'th something... - Mrs. Hannagan!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.92,0:33:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 好的 - 等一下{\r}\N[Sighs] - Yeah. - Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.33,0:33:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我到哪里才能找到 休奎奇的儿子?{\r}\NThis Shoebridge son... where do I look for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.96,0:33:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}嗯,到巴洛溪公墓试试吧{\r}\NWell, try the Barlow Creek Cemetery.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.96,0:33:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 什么意思,到公墓? - 嗯,我不确定,但我认为他死了{\r}\N- What do you mean, the cemetery? - Well, I'm not sure, but I think he's dead, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.44,0:35:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}抱歉!{\r}\NSorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.40,0:35:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}(哈利・休奎奇、莎蒂・休奎奇){\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.00,0:35:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}(艾迪・休奎奇){\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.56,0:35:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}死胡同,布兰琪{\r}\N[Shovel Scraping] Dead end, Blanche.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.79,0:35:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}早就埋葬了{\r}\NDead and buried.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.29,0:36:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我是管理人,能为你做什么吗? - 我是这家庭的朋友{\r}\N- Caretaker. Do somethir for you? - I'm a friend of the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.66,0:36:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}什么都没留下,这差事糟透了{\r}\NNone left. Bad business, that.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.16,0:36:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你是指大火吗?{\r}\NYou mean the fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.77,0:36:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不喜欢他们同时被埋葬{\r}\NNever liked them multiple funerals.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.77,0:36:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}太多工作都挤在同一时间{\r}\NToo much work involved, all at one time.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.14,0:36:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他们是一起死的 但他们没有埋在一起{\r}\NThey died together, yet they're not...\Nburied together in the same hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.68,0:36:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}为什么?{\r}\NHow come?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.25,0:36:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我怎么知道{\r}\NSearch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.79,0:36:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}瞧这里{\r}\NHere. Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.77,0:36:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}1950年过世{\r}\NDied in 1950. Died 1950.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.77,0:36:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}1950年过世{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.64,0:36:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这两个死亡日期相同{\r}\NBoth died the same date.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.31,0:37:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}旧石碑{\r}\NOld stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.38,0:37:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}而这个是新的石碑{\r}\NThis is practically new stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.48,0:37:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 真是聪明人 - 怎么? 被我发现什么了?{\r}\N- Smart fellow, ain't ya? - Why? Have I stumbled on to something?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.49,0:37:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}哦,很高兴认识你{\r}\NWell, nice meetir ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.93,0:37:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我该回去干活了 明天在这儿还有份工作{\r}\NBetter get back to my work. I got a job comir in here tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.52,0:37:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}把那该死的东西关小,玛西洛{\r}\NTurn that damn thing down, Marcella.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.52,0:37:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我甚至听不到自己的说话声{\r}\NCan't even hear myself think. [Fades]
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.09,0:37:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你想我怎么可能 记得那么久以前的事情?{\r}\NHow do you expect me to remember anything that far back?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.43,0:37:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我必须要翻阅我的旧档案 来找资料才行{\r}\NI'd have to go through my old files for that kind of information.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.66,0:37:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}嗯,威勒先生,我不喜欢坚持…{\r}\NWell, Mr. Wheeler, I hate to insist...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.13,0:37:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你知道吗? 麦克布莱先生{\r}\N[Chiseling, Music Continue] You know something, Mr. McBride?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.94,0:37:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你们律师全都一样{\r}\NYou lawyers are all alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.10,0:38:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}麻烦,麻烦,麻烦{\r}\NTrouble, trouble, trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.21,0:38:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}来吧,我可没有整天的时间{\r}\NWell, come on. I don't have all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.21,0:38:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你说的那一家是哪一年死的?{\r}\NWhat year did you say the family died?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.05,0:38:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}嗯…1950年{\r}\NUh, 1950.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.48,0:38:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}几月?{\r}\N[Groans] What month?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.55,0:38:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 这我可帮不了你 - 休奎奇,休奎…{\r}\NAh, I can't help you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.55,0:38:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我能坐下吗? - 好,请便{\r}\N- Shoebridge. Shoebri... - Can I sit down? - Yeah, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.86,0:38:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}休奎奇,休奎奇{\r}\NShoebridge. Shoebridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.43,0:38:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}喔,在这儿 "休奎奇,哈利和莎蒂"{\r}\NOh, here it is. "Shoebridge: Harry and Sadie.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.00,0:38:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}"大型大理石,28号"{\r}\N"Large marble. Model 28.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.07,0:38:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}"全额支付,检索编号93"{\r}\N"Paid in full. Check number 93.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.57,0:38:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}"第一教堂末世圣徒,巴洛溪"{\r}\NFirst Church of Latter Day Saints, Barlow Creek."
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.78,0:38:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那儿子呢?{\r}\NWhat about the son?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.78,0:38:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 艾迪・休奎奇,他们的儿子 - 艾迪?{\r}\N- Edward Shoebridge. He's their son. - Edward?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.01,0:38:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 是的 - 好…不{\r}\N- Yeah. - Okay. Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.18,0:38:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 没有 - 什么意思,没有?{\r}\N- Nothing. - What do you mean, nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.02,0:38:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}肯定有,或许他比较晚来{\r}\NThere's gotta be something. Maybe it came later.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.72,0:38:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}等等,你是说艾迪・休奎奇 他的墓碑? 是的,他比较晚来{\r}\NWait a minute. You're talking about Eddie Shoebridge.\NHis headstone? Yeah, that did come later. [Coughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.69,0:38:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我想是,嗯…65号{\r}\NI think in, uh, '65.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.43,0:39:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是的,我记得那孩子{\r}\NSure, I remember that kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.60,0:39:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他在这里太受欢迎 有人说是他自己放的火{\r}\NHe wasrt too popular around here. Some say he set that fire himself...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.50,0:39:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}为了摆脱他的家人然后消失{\r}\Nto get rid of his family, and then disappeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.67,0:39:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}使他看起来 像是也在大火中丧生{\r}\Nto make it look like he died in the fire too.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.64,0:39:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 他们从来没发现他的尸体 - 你是说没有尸体在他的坟墓中?{\r}\N- They never did find his body. - You mean, there's no body in that grave?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.61,0:39:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}嗯,我记得 这就是为什么当地的牧师…{\r}\NWell, as I recollect, that's why the local parson...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.15,0:39:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}没有为艾迪做任何事的原因{\r}\Nwouldn't say any services for Eddie.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.32,0:39:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}没有死亡证明吗?{\r}\NWell, [Coughs] Wasrt there a death certificate?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.29,0:39:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不知道,我也不需要知道{\r}\NI wouldn't know about that. And I don't need to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.49,0:39:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我只是个生意人,麦克布莱先生{\r}\NI'm just a businessman, Mr. McBride.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.69,0:39:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}啊,在这儿{\r}\N- [Sighs] - Ah, here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.53,0:39:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}"艾迪・休奎奇,特级花岗岩"{\r}\N"Edward Shoebridge. Granite special.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.90,0:39:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}"11月12日订制"{\r}\N"Ordered, November 12.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.24,0:39:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}"1965年11月18日支付"{\r}\N"Paid for, November 18, 1965.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.91,0:39:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}"395美元"{\r}\N$395."
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.34,0:39:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}有趣的是,他以现金支付{\r}\NNow, that's funny. It's paid in cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.71,0:39:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 他们通常不会这样做 - 那是谁?{\r}\N- They don't usually do that. - Who was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.82,0:39:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不知道,麦克布莱先生{\r}\NI don't know, Mr. McBride.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.82,0:39:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我猜他不想让人知道他的名字{\r}\NI guess he didn't want his name known.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.42,0:39:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}什么意思"他"?{\r}\NWell, what do you mean, he?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.99,0:40:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你刚才说"他" - 我有说吗?{\r}\N- You just said he. - I did, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.40,0:40:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}哦,你知道的 我依稀记得好像…是个男人{\r}\NWell, you know, I seem to sort of remember...\Nthat it was a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.07,0:40:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}对了,年轻小伙子{\r}\NYeah. A young fella.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.61,0:40:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}微秃,我猜他20多岁{\r}\NSlightly bald. I'd say in his late twenties.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.64,0:40:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你有没有再见到他,嗯… 安置墓碑的时候?{\r}\NAnd did you see him again when you, uh...\N[Scratches Paper] Put in the headstone?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.02,0:40:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们并没有这样做 是他自己来把墓碑带走的{\r}\NWe didn't do that. He came by and picked it up himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.15,0:40:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}对,我想起来了,用一辆拖车{\r}\NYes, I remember now. In one of those tow trucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.86,0:40:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你知道,那种拖车库的? - 我知道{\r}\N- You know, the kind that garages use? - Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.80,0:40:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}(出生死亡登记处){\r}\N[Typing, Chattering]
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.27,0:40:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不,这里没有 艾迪・休奎奇的死亡证明{\r}\NNo, there is no death certificate here for Edward Shoebridge,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.00,0:40:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}只有哈利・休奎奇和 莎蒂・休奎奇的{\r}\Nonly Harry J. Shoebridge and Sadie L. Shoebridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.64,0:40:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}就只有这样?{\r}\NThat's all you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.54,0:40:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}哦,这里还有{\r}\NWell, there is this.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.85,0:40:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}似乎曾有人为艾迪・休奎奇 申请死亡证明书{\r}\NIt appears to be an application for a death certificate...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.75,0:41:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}日期是1965年11月4日{\r}\Nfor one Edward Shoebridge, dated November 4, 1965.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.12,0:41:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}"由于申请人无提供任何死亡证据"{\r}\N"Inasmuch as applicant could furnish no proof of death...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.72,0:41:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}"当事人的尸体一直未被寻获"{\r}\N"for party whose body had never been found,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.73,0:41:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}"没有提供医疗死亡证明书"{\r}\N"and who could supply no medical death certificate,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.33,0:41:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}"亦没有法医检验,该申请被拒绝"{\r}\N"and nothing from the coroner's office, the application was denied.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.13,0:41:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}"申请人接获通知后可到法院诉讼"{\r}\N"Applicant, when informed he could file a petition for court action,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.90,0:41:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}"但拒绝了这项建议"{\r}\Ndeclined the suggestion."
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.47,0:41:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}有说申请人是谁吗?{\r}\NDoes it say who the applicant was?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.84,0:41:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}有,"申请人乔森・马洛尼"{\r}\NYes. "Request was made by Joseph P. Maloney,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.68,0:41:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}"巴洛溪426大街"{\r}\N426 Main Street, Barlow Creek."
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.15,0:41:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 很好,谢谢你 - 不客气{\r}\N- Attagirl. Thank you. - You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.70,0:42:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}(J・马洛尼){\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.82,0:42:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 加满? - 麻烦你{\r}\N- Fill 'er up? - Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.94,0:43:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你要检查引擎吗? - 如果你可以,麻烦你{\r}\N- You want to check under the hood? - If you would, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.55,0:43:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 小心火柴 - 喔,好的{\r}\N- Better be careful with those matches. - Oh. Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.35,0:43:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}抱歉{\r}\NSorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.73,0:43:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 这店是你开的? - 是啊{\r}\NThis your place? [Dinging] Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.40,0:43:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那你一定就是"J・马洛尼"{\r}\NThen you must be, uh, "J. Maloney."
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.53,0:43:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}告诉我,这是代表,嗯… 约翰・马洛尼?{\r}\NTell me, does that stand for, uh, John orJim? [Dinging]
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.07,0:43:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 乔森 - 是的{\r}\N- Joe. - Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.81,0:43:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}一切正常{\r}\N[Pumping Stops] Everything's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.62,0:43:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}有趣,嗯…你几乎不需要任何油{\r}\NFunny, uh, you didn't hardly need any gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.22,0:43:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不需要加油… 我猜你来这里不是为了车,先生?{\r}\NDidrt need no oil... Guess you didn't come here for the car, huh, mister?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.96,0:43:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你能帮我擦一下挡风玻璃吗?{\r}\NCould you get my windshield, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.96,0:43:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}没问题{\r}\NDon't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.50,0:44:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你知道一个叫做 艾迪・休奎奇的人吗?{\r}\NYou wouldn't happen to know a guy by the name of Edward Shoebridge, would ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.77,0:44:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}以前住在这一边{\r}\NUsed to live around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.54,0:44:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这名字我没印象{\r}\NName don't ring no bell with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.58,0:44:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}为什么你要问这个 嗯,他叫什么…休奎奇?{\r}\NWhat would you be wantir with this, uh, what's his name, uh, Shoebridge?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.91,0:44:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是啊,法律问题{\r}\NYeah. Legal matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.45,0:44:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你是律师? - 对{\r}\N- You a lawyer? - Yeah. [Coughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.22,0:44:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我叫麦克布莱 法兰克・麦克布莱{\r}\NName's McBride. Frank McBride.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.36,0:44:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我第一次和不需要 我付钱的律师交谈{\r}\N- First time I ever talked to a lawyer didn't cost me money. - [Chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.29,0:44:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}实际上,马洛尼先生 和我交谈还能让你赚点钱{\r}\NActually, Mr. Maloney, by talking to me you could make yourself some money.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.03,0:44:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 是吗? - 我愿意支付合理的现金{\r}\N- Yeah? - I'm prepared to pay a reasonable sum of cash,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.44,0:44:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}立刻付,如果你能提供给我任何 艾迪・休奎奇的资讯{\r}\Nright now, for any information that could lead me to Eddie Shoebridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.47,0:44:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我到任何地方 律师通常是带来坏消息{\r}\NWhere I come from, lawyers are usually bad news.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.68,0:44:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}喔,不,这次不是 这次会是个好消息{\r}\NOh, no. Not this time. This time they're good news.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.35,0:44:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}事实上,我认为艾迪・休奎奇 会很高兴听到我带给他的消息{\r}\NMatter of fact, I think that Eddie Shoebridge...\Nwould be delighted when he hears from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.65,0:44:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你要告诉他什么?{\r}\NWhat are you gonna tell him?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.85,0:44:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}嗯,我的客户要求我保密{\r}\NWell, my client has asked me to keep that confidential.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.36,0:45:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}谁聘请你去找这家伙?{\r}\NWho hired you to find this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.26,0:45:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 这也得保密 - 我当然希望能帮你,先生…{\r}\N- That's confidential also. - Sure like to help you, Mister...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.86,0:45:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这里的生意并不太好{\r}\NBusiness ain't all that good around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.20,0:45:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我想你能帮我 - 是吗?{\r}\N- I think you can help me. - Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.57,0:45:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}嗯,这里的人们告诉我 艾迪・休奎奇已经死了{\r}\NMm-hmm. See, people around here have been telling me that Eddie Shoebridge is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.07,0:45:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如果他死了,看来他就听不到 你要告诉他的好消息了,嗯?{\r}\N[Sighs] Well, if he's dead, looks like he ain't gonna be hearir...\Nall that good news you have to tell him, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.35,0:45:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我认为他还活着{\r}\NI think he's alive.\N[Sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.62,0:45:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}看来这辆车不需要太干净了{\r}\NSure don't keep this car very clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.65,0:45:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你能告诉我,为什么要在空坟上 安置墓碑吗? 马洛尼{\r}\NYou want to tell me why you put a headstone on an empty grave, Maloney?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.42,0:45:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}什么墓碑?{\r}\NWhat headstone?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.69,0:45:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}一个你付了395美元买的 就在1965年{\r}\NThe one you paid $395 for back in 1965.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.30,0:45:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你欠我2.47美元,先生{\r}\NYou owe me $2.47, mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.60,0:45:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}两个星期前,你到县政府申请 艾迪・休奎奇的死亡证明{\r}\NTwo weeks before that, you went to the county courthouse...\Nand asked for a certificate of death for Edward Shoebridge,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.54,0:45:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}而且你被拒绝了{\r}\Nand you were turned down.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.78,0:45:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你要用信用卡支付吗? - 不{\r}\N-You wanna give me your credit card? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.82,0:46:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}信用卡被停用了{\r}\NCredit cards are out.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.06,0:46:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}跟你一样,我喜欢付…现金{\r}\NLike you, I prefer to pay... in cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.52,0:46:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这个是我个人最喜欢的{\r}\NNow, this one happens to be my personal favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.42,0:46:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是不是很高雅?{\r}\NIsn't it exquisite?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.96,0:46:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}对我来说太贵了{\r}\N[Woman] Probably too expensive for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.83,0:46:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我能帮你吗? 先生{\r}\N[Bell Dings] [Woman #2] Can I help you, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.53,0:46:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}抱歉,我马上回来{\r}\NExcuse me. I'll be right back. Uh, Mrs. Clay?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.34,0:46:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}克莱儿女士,你能帮我 接待一下坎妮安女士吗?{\r}\NWould you take care of Mrs. Cunningham for a few moments?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.94,0:46:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好的,亚当森先生{\r}\NCertainly, Mr. Adamson.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.75,0:47:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我担心我太过喜欢了{\r}\N[Mrs. Cunningham] I'm afraid I rather like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.12,0:47:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}嘿,艾迪,你这狗娘养的{\r}\N[Joe] Hey, Eddie. You old son of a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.22,0:47:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如果对你来说都一样 我比较喜欢叫亚瑟・亚当森{\r}\NIf it's all the same to you, I prefer Arthur Adamson.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.99,0:47:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你来这里干嘛?{\r}\NNow what in the hell are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.73,0:47:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}有要紧的事找你 就这样,艾迪…亚瑟{\r}\NHad to see you about something kind of urgent. That's all, Eddie... Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.30,0:47:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你就不能打电话给我吗? - 有些事不能在电话里谈{\r}\N- Couldrt you have phoned me? - Some things you don't put on no telephone.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.80,0:47:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}嘿,你有酒吗?{\r}\NHey, uh, you got any booze around?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.78,0:47:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好吧,乔森,这次是什么事?{\r}\NAll right, Joseph. What is it this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.51,0:47:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}要买新的冰箱给你老婆?{\r}\N[Pouring Drink] New freezer for your wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.18,0:47:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}老妈要做另一个手术? 赌徒威胁要杀你? 还是什么?{\r}\NMother needs another operation? Bookies threatened to kill you? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.12,0:47:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}嘿,艾迪,你把我说得好像寄生虫{\r}\NAw, come on, Eddie. You make me sound like some kind of sponger.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.96,0:47:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不是不感激你的帮助{\r}\NNot that I ain't grateful for all your favors.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.99,0:47:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我有得选择吗? - 好了,好了,就这样{\r}\N- Did I ever have a choice? - Okay, okay. Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.16,0:47:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}首先,我得问你一个问题{\r}\N[Sniffs] First off, I gotta ask you a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.37,0:47:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 问吧 - 我问你,别废话,艾迪{\r}\N- Go ahead. - I'm tellir ya. No shit now, Eddie.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.37,0:48:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你能想到什么理由,这么多年后 怎么会有人对你的生活感兴趣?{\r}\NCan you think of any reason why anyone would be sniffir around in your life...\Nafter all these years?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.91,0:48:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我想不出任何理由,怎么了?{\r}\NI can't think of any reason at all. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.35,0:48:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}今天有个家伙来到车厂{\r}\NWell, there's this guy comes around the garage today...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.89,0:48:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}探问艾迪・休奎奇{\r}\Ntryir to locate Eddie Shoebridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.22,0:48:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他自称是个律师 有个好消息带给你{\r}\NClaims he's a lawyer, he's got good news for ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.52,0:48:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}没说是什么事,为谁工作{\r}\NWort say what, or who he's workir for.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.36,0:48:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}只说他叫麦克布莱 我第一眼看到他就知道是说谎{\r}\NCalls himself McBride. I know he's a phony the minute I see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.86,0:48:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 警察? - 不,是业余的{\r}\N- Police? - No way. He's a real amateur.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.00,0:48:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我追查他的车牌{\r}\NI traced his license plates with the bureau...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.50,0:48:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}也不是开他自己的车{\r}\NDoesrt even drive his own car.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.98,0:48:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}"布兰琪・泰勒,城堡大道17号"{\r}\N"Blanche Tyler, 17 Castle Heights Road."
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.88,0:48:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 他长什么样子? - 高瘦,大约35岁{\r}\N- What did he look like? - [Coughs] He's tall, thin, about 35.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.25,0:48:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他叼着一支烟斗 问许多自以为是的问题{\r}\NHe's always got a pipe on. Asking a lot of smart-ass questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.86,0:48:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你告诉他什么了? - 什么该死的都没说{\r}\N- What'd you tell him? - Nothir. Not a goddamn thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.53,0:48:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不需要说,他什么都知道{\r}\NI didn't have to. He knew everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.53,0:48:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你叫我帮你立的假墓碑{\r}\Nfake headstone you had me put up,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.87,0:49:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我如何试图帮你申请死亡证明{\r}\Nhow I tried to get you officially declared dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.80,0:49:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那狗娘养的还说了 他认为你还活着{\r}\NThe son of a bitch says he thinks you're still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.27,0:49:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他在找你,艾迪{\r}\NHe's lookir for you, Eddie.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.11,0:49:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}任何一个狗娘养的想找到你{\r}\NAnd any son of a bitch who's lookir for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.84,0:49:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}就会找上我{\r}\Nis lookir for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.38,0:49:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}哦…{\r}\NWell,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.39,0:49:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}无论他有什么行动 他不会找到我的{\r}\Nwhatever he's up to, he won't find me.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.06,0:49:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你太过担心了,乔森{\r}\NYou worry too much, Joseph.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.79,0:49:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是呀,我太过担心 因为你只是策划放火{\r}\NYeah, I worry too much, because you only planned the fire,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.06,0:49:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}把老先生和老太太锁在卧房里{\r}\Nand locked your old man and old lady in the bedroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.03,0:49:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 是我淋汽油,我点燃抹布 - 我很感谢你{\r}\N- I poured the gasoline. I lit the rags. - And I thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.64,0:49:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那是我不光彩的童年当中 最快乐的一天{\r}\NThe happiest day of my whole, inglorious childhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.47,0:49:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好吧,你想继续当孩子 我有我的做法{\r}\NAll right, you want to kid about it, it's all right with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.98,0:49:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我要跟踪这家伙 - 然后呢?{\r}\N- I'm gonna track this guy down. - And then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.92,0:49:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这个…{\r}\NThis.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.15,0:49:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你永远不会改变,是吗? - 你有没有理由抱怨{\r}\N- You'll never change, will you? - You got no cause to complain.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.79,0:50:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 当你需要我,我总是在那里 - 听着,把那东西拿开{\r}\N- When you needed me, I was always there, wasrt I? - Look, put that thing away.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.00,0:50:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}听我说,我要你回巴洛溪{\r}\NAnd listen to me. I want you to go back to Barlow Creek.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.63,0:50:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}什么都别做,什么都别说{\r}\NDo nothing, say nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.63,0:50:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}让我自己来解决这件事 用平静的方式{\r}\NLet me look into this matter in my own, quiet way.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.27,0:50:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如果我需要你,我会和你联络{\r}\NAnd if I need you for anything, I'll contact you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.28,0:50:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好吗?{\r}\NOkay?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.85,0:50:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你是老板,亚瑟{\r}\NYou're the boss, Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.99,0:50:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这很感人不是吗… 一个完美的谋杀…{\r}\NIsn't it touching how... a perfect murder...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.89,0:50:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}使我们的友谊 这些年来一直维系着?{\r}\Nhas kept our friendship alive all these years?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.83,0:50:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你最好相信{\r}\NYou better believe it. [Knocking At Door]
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.20,0:50:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}抱歉,打扰了,亚当森先生{\r}\N- [Door Opens] - I'm sorry to disturb you, Mr. Adamson.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.87,0:50:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}有两位先生找您,从警局来的{\r}\NThere are two gentlemen here to see you, from the police department.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.11,0:50:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}告诉他们,我马上来{\r}\NTell them I'll be right out.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.84,0:50:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}老天,艾迪{\r}\N[Door Closes] Jesus Christ, Eddie!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.01,0:50:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}在这儿等着{\r}\N[Softly] Wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.56,0:51:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我是亚瑟・亚当森,能为您效劳? - 抱歉,打扰您{\r}\NArthur Adamson. What can I do for you gentlemen? Sorry to bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.50,0:51:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我是安迪・布希检察官 这位是彼得森副官{\r}\NAndy Bush, Bureau of Inspectors, and this is Lieutenant Peterson.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.30,0:51:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 嗨 - 我的荣幸{\r}\NHi. My pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.30,0:51:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}毫无疑问,你一定读过或听说过 康斯坦丁绑架案{\r}\NNo doubt you've been reading, or hearing, about the Constantine kidnapping.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.31,0:51:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}哦,我必须承认,检察官{\r}\NWell, I have a confession to make, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.61,0:51:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}当我听到那宝石的大小 我都流口水了{\r}\NWhen I heard of the size of that stone, my mouth watered.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.71,0:51:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}专业来说{\r}\NProfessionally speaking, of course. [Chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.48,0:51:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}希望你不要感到受歧视 亚当森先生{\r}\NWell, just so you don't feel discriminated against, Mr. Adamson,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.12,0:51:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们只是对城里的每个珠宝商 和银楼做例行性询问{\r}\Nwe're routinely covering every gem dealer and jewelry store in the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.49,0:51:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}哦,我受宠若惊{\r}\NWell, I'm flattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.49,0:51:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你有许多机会去接触 有注意到什么不寻常吗?{\r}\NHave you, by any chance, noticed anything out of the ordinary, Mr. Adamson?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.53,0:51:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}有任何异常的大小宝石 在过去几天流入市面?{\r}\NAny unusual movement of large... or small... stones into the markets these last few days?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.14,0:51:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 绝对没有 - 我明白了{\r}\N- Absolutely not. - I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.14,0:51:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我认为你们可以假设这个,嗯… "赃物"已经被切割成较小的宝石{\r}\NI take it that you're going on the assumption...\Nthat this, uh, "ransom stone" has been cut up into smaller gems?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.31,0:52:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 有道理,先生 - 这样更有销路{\r}\N- That's correct, sir. - It makes a lot of sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.41,0:52:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们也是这么认为{\r}\NWe think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.45,0:52:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如果可以 恕我冒昧地提出一项建议{\r}\NIf I may presume to make a suggestion,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.02,0:52:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}在我看来,你们应该涵盖 古董商和二手珠宝市场{\r}\Nit seems to me you ought to be covering the antique and secondhand jewelry markets.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.42,0:52:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他们从任何人那里购买 而我们只向专业珠宝批发商买货{\r}\NThey buy from anyone, whereas we jewelers buy exclusively on the wholesale exchanges.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.63,0:52:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我们已经这么做了,亚当森先生 - 喔{\r}\N- That's already being done, Mr. Adamson. - Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.87,0:52:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我认为我们已经占用 亚当森先生太多时间了{\r}\NI think we've taken up enough of Mr. Adamsors time.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.27,0:52:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}很抱歉,我没能给你们 太多的帮助{\r}\NWell, I'm sorry I haven't been able to be of more help to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.67,0:52:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不过,如果我有听到任何 不寻常的市场交易{\r}\NHowever, if I do hear of any unusual transactions in the marketplace,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.38,0:52:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我一定会与您联系{\r}\NI'll be sure and contact you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.38,0:52:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 好的,不胜感激,再见 - 保重{\r}\N- Yes, we'd appreciate that. Much obliged. - Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.32,0:52:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 再见,先生 - 祝你们好运{\r}\N- Good-bye, sir. - Good day. And good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.34,0:53:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}克莱儿女士,你可以关门了 我还有一些工作要做{\r}\NMrs. Clay, close up as soon as you wish. I have some work to do in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.97,0:53:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我会从后门离开{\r}\NI'll let myself out the back way.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.24,0:53:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 晚安 - 晚安{\r}\NGood night. Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.50,0:53:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}(布兰琪・泰勒,城堡大道17号){\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.70,0:53:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}(城堡大道){\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.25,0:54:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你的朋友布兰琪・泰勒是个灵媒 - 灵媒?{\r}\N- Your friend, Blanche Tyler, is a spiritualist. - A spiritualist?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.65,0:54:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}招牌上是这么写的 但没有人在家{\r}\NThat's what it says on her shingle. Also, there's no one home.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.02,0:54:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}灵魂是永远不会在家的,上车{\r}\NA spirit is never at home. Get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.40,0:54:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你认为我们该怎么办?{\r}\N[Sighs] What do you think we should do?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.90,0:54:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们等待 我们仍然不知道那男的是谁{\r}\NWe'll wait. We still don't know who the man is yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.84,0:54:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 非抽不可? - 嗯哼{\r}\NMust you? Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.22,0:54:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那一定是她{\r}\NThat must be her.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.38,0:55:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那个叼着烟斗的 肯定就是去找马洛尼的人{\r}\NThat must be the fellow with the pipe who called on Maloney.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.05,0:55:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}一个计程车司机{\r}\NA cab driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.02,0:55:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}鲁尼,鲁尼,怎么回事? 你要去哪儿?{\r}\NLumley. Lumley, what's this? Where are ya goir?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.79,0:55:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我要回家躺在自己的床上 可以好好睡个觉{\r}\NI'm going home to my own bed where I can get some sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.99,0:55:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不,你不会的{\r}\NNo, you're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.60,0:55:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}布兰琪,你不能每件事 都要顺着你的意{\r}\NBlanche, is that all you've ever got on your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.47,0:55:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你留着要干嘛,未雨绸缪?{\r}\NWhat are you saving it for, a rainy day?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.90,0:55:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}亲爱的,你永远不会知道 什么时候会需要它{\r}\NHoney, you never know when you're gonna need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.00,0:55:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你很不体贴,鲁尼{\r}\NYou're not being friendly, Lumley.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.21,0:55:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}布兰琪,我已经精疲力尽了 我对你是没利用价值的{\r}\NBlanche, I'm too pooped to pop. I'd be useless to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.41,0:55:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你对我总是毫无用处{\r}\NYou're always useless to me! [Dog Barking]
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.78,0:55:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}当我需要你时,你总是精疲力尽!{\r}\NYou're always pooping out when I need you! [Car Horn Honking]
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.32,0:56:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们可以赚一大笔钱 你说这是毫无用处?{\r}\N[George] ... we can collect a huge sum of money, : You call that useless?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.22,0:56:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你知道我在说什么 来,进屋吧,别吵了{\r}\NYou know what I'm talking about. Come on in side and stop being difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.42,0:56:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}今晚不行,我不会留在这儿{\r}\NNot tonight, Josephine. I'm outta here.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.56,0:56:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你这个懒虫!{\r}\N- You're a fink! - If I'm a fink, you're an ungrateful bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.05,0:56:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如果我是懒虫 你就是一个忘恩负义的婊子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.63,0:56:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 那明天呢? - 怎样?{\r}\NWhat about tomorrow? What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.06,0:56:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你有重要的工作要做 我要你确认谁是艾迪・休奎…{\r}\NYou've got important work to do. I want you to be sure about Eddie Shoe...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.47,0:56:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}跟他说!{\r}\N- [Passing Car Obscures Dialog] - Talk to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.80,0:56:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你要告诉我多少次?{\r}\NHow many times are you going to tell me that?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.21,0:56:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我又要告诉你多少次 我明天的工作是开计程车?{\r}\NHow many times am I gonna have to tell you that tomorrow I have to work in my cab?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.18,0:56:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}所以要等到礼拜天{\r}\NSo it'll wait till Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.93,0:56:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你最好给我一个简要 我一头雾水{\r}\NYou better give me a quick synopsis. I'm confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.40,0:56:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}很简单,一个疲惫的计程车司机{\r}\NSimple. A cab driver is shacked up...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.74,0:56:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}和一个性饥渴的灵媒 布兰琪・泰勒{\r}\Nwith a sex-starved medium named Blanche Tyler.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.20,0:56:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}别问我为什么,但很显然 他们找到了艾迪・休奎奇的幽灵{\r}\NDon't ask me why, but apparently they're on the trail...\Nof some spook named Eddie Shoebridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.91,0:57:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}幸运的是,不是在追踪 你最喜欢的"赃物"和我{\r}\NFortunately, not on the trail of your favorite kidnapper and mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.08,0:57:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你怎么能那么肯定?{\r}\NHow can you be so sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.08,0:57:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你也听到了 他们谈论到将赚一大笔钱{\r}\NYou did hear him talk about collecting a huge hunk of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.05,0:57:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那报酬不是在我们头上?{\r}\NCouldrt that be the reward that's on our heads?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.92,0:57:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你说到重点了,法兰西大姊{\r}\NYou got yourself a point there, Frances, old girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.52,0:57:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}只有时间才能告诉我们 是好是坏{\r}\NOnly time will tell whether it's any good.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.43,0:57:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但有一件事是肯定的{\r}\NOne thing's certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.43,0:57:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们不会改变我们的计划 不会是现在{\r}\NWe're not going to change our game plan. Not now.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.67,0:57:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}买瓶酒给我,亚瑟{\r}\NBuy me a drink, Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.17,0:57:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}一辆闪亮的车{\r}\NA shiny car.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.07,0:57:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}一辆豪华轿车?{\r}\NA... limousine?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.94,0:57:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他为什么要开得这么快,亨利?{\r}\NWhy does he drive so fast, Henry?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.45,0:57:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那是什么? 在他旁边座位上的?{\r}\NWhat's that? On the seat beside him?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.51,0:57:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我听到婴儿的哭声 快,亨利,在他消失前{\r}\NI hear the sound of a baby crying. Quick, Henry, before he disappears.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.15,0:57:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}问他…是的,我明白{\r}\NAsk... Yes, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.52,0:57:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我…看到他了{\r}\NI... see him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.93,0:57:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}穿着制服,一个司机{\r}\NThe uniform. A chauffeur.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.77,0:57:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}什么? 亨利,我要听他说话{\r}\NWhat? Henry, I need words.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.47,0:57:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}谁? 什么?{\r}\NWho? The what?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.47,0:58:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}兰伯特家的司机?{\r}\N[Panting] The Rainbird chauffeur?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.84,0:58:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}天哪,老麦克・欧基夫 我们的司机{\r}\NGood heavens. Old Michael O'Keefe, our chauffeur.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.54,0:58:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}麦克要去哪里?{\r}\N[Gasps] Where is Michael going?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.41,0:58:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}亨利,问他把哈丽叶的婴儿 带去哪里?{\r}\NHenry, ask him where he's taking Harriet's baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.48,0:58:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}噢,有太多影像,闪得太快了{\r}\NOh, more pictures are coming in too fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.29,0:58:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我看不清楚{\r}\NI can hardly make them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.06,0:58:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}亨利,墓地,一个墓碑?{\r}\NHenry, a graveyard, a headstone?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.43,0:58:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不喜欢这样,亨利{\r}\NI don't like this, Henry.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.86,0:58:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}鞋子…桥…{\r}\NA shoe. Bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.87,0:58:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}鞋子桥? (音似休奎奇) 噢,不要这样对我,亨利{\r}\NA shoe bridge? Oh, don't do this to me, Henry.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.10,0:58:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 对司机说话 - 噢,上帝,有东西在燃烧{\r}\N- Speak to the chauffeur. - Oh, God, something's burning.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.77,0:58:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是房子,快,亨利,房子着火了{\r}\NThe house. Quick, Henry. The house is on fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.78,0:58:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}带我离开这里{\r}\NTake me away from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.18,0:58:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不想看这些{\r}\NI don't want to see this.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.21,0:58:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我受不了他们可怕的尖叫声{\r}\NI can't bear the sound of their awful screaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.89,0:58:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}回到司机那里,亨利 让麦克加入我们{\r}\NGo back to the chauffeur, Henry. Get Michael into our presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.12,0:58:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}兰伯特女士记得他{\r}\NMiss Rainbird remembers him.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.22,0:58:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是的,我记得{\r}\NYes, I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.39,0:58:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}布兰琪夫人,让我来说{\r}\NMadame Blanche, listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.13,0:59:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你能听到我吗?{\r}\NCan you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.03,0:59:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我想起一件事,这非常重要{\r}\NI've remembered something else that could be terribly important.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.17,0:59:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}等一下,亨利,在你走之前{\r}\NWait one minute, Henry. Before you go,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.61,0:59:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}兰伯特女士需要知道 哈丽叶孩子的情况{\r}\NMiss Rainbird deserves some kind of assurance about Harriet's child.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.91,0:59:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他现在是个大人了{\r}\NHe's a man by now,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.68,0:59:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们想知道他现在快乐吗?{\r}\Nand we have to know, is he happy, Henry?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.15,0:59:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他还活着吗? 过得幸福吗?{\r}\NIs he alive and well and happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.29,0:59:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如果你不能…{\r}\NIf you can't, you can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.59,0:59:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我当然不能强迫你{\r}\NI certainly can't force you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.36,0:59:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是,当然,她会理解的{\r}\NYes. Of course she'll understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.50,0:59:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}直到下一次,那么,再见了{\r}\NUntil next time, then. Good-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.70,0:59:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}再见,亲爱的{\r}\NGood-bye, my love.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.24,0:59:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 发生什么事? - 难道你不记得了?{\r}\N- What happened? - Don't you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.68,0:59:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 并不太愉快 - 噢,没关系了{\r}\N- Not a blessed thing. - Oh, it doesn't matter now.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.55,0:59:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}听着,听着,布兰琪夫人{\r}\NListen, listen, Madame Blanche.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.09,0:59:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你的亨利拾回了 我完全遗忘的记忆{\r}\NYour Henry jogged my memory of something I'd completely forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.79,1:00:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}当我们可怜的老司机麦克 意识到他即将死亡时{\r}\NWhen our poor old chauffeur, Mike, realized he was dying,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.93,1:00:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他写信给我,说世上有个人…{\r}\Nhe wrote to me and said there was one person on earth...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.13,1:00:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他许下承诺说{\r}\Nwho had promised that he'd make it his business...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.04,1:00:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}只要他还活着 就能够知道哈丽叶的儿子在哪儿{\r}\Nto know where Harriet's son was as long as he lived.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.54,1:00:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是个牧师,帮新生婴儿洗礼的{\r}\NIt was the parson who baptized the newborn baby.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.81,1:00:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}还有一件事我要告诉你…{\r}\NAnd there's an additional thing I can tell you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.65,1:00:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}别告诉我,让我猜猜看{\r}\NDon't tell me. Let me guess.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.25,1:00:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 500美元 - 没钱,连100也没有{\r}\N- Five hundred. - Not a penny. Not even a hundred for expenses.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.79,1:00:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这是全有或全无,乔治{\r}\NIt's all or nothing, George,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.79,1:00:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}直到我可以找出 他的名字和现在的住址{\r}\Nuntil I can produce his name and his present address.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.33,1:00:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 老天,布兰琪 - 不过,她给了我一条重大线索{\r}\N- Jesus, Blanche. - However, she gave me a marvelous clue.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.53,1:00:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我们又来了 - 不,是你有得忙了…{\r}\N- Here we go again. - No, here you go again...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.50,1:00:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}有一个人可以告诉你 休奎奇是生是死{\r}\Nto the man who might tell you if Shoebridge is dead or alive.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.54,1:00:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 那是谁? - 圣安塞尔姆大教堂的伍德主教{\r}\N- Who's that? - Bishop Wood at St. Anselm's Cathedral.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.68,1:00:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 老天爷,布兰琪 - 不,乔治,不是k{\r}\N- Holy Christ, Blanche. - No, George, not him.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.61,1:00:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是圣安塞尔姆大教堂的伍德主教{\r}\NBishop Wood at St. Anselm's Cathedral.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.25,1:01:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他曾经是一个牧师 替婴儿时期的休奎奇受洗过{\r}\NHe was a parson once and he baptized the Shoebridge baby.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.50,1:01:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}打扰一下{\r}\NExcuse me.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.27,1:01:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}抱歉{\r}\NSorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.31,1:02:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你知道我要怎样 才能约见伍德主教?{\r}\NDo you know how I could, uh, make a date to see Bishop Wood?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.71,1:02:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如果你想今天约见 你必须先找牧师{\r}\NIf you want to make the appointment today, you'll have to make it through the chaplain.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.78,1:02:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}哪一个是牧师?{\r}\NWhich one is the chaplain?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:08.35,1:02:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}礼拜结束后,我会带你去的{\r}\NWhen the service is over, I'll show you where to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.41,1:02:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}噢,亲爱的{\r}\NOh, dear.\N[Congregation Chattering]
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.75,1:03:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你知道他还在动 你确定给他的用量足够?{\r}\NYou know he's moving. You sure you gave him enough?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.52,1:03:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}只是一般的剂量 他看起来无害{\r}\NJust the usual dose. He looks so harmless.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.26,1:03:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}当我还是个孩子时 住在这个村庄{\r}\NWhen I was a little kid living in that village,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.43,1:03:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他总是让我觉得 我是个邪恶的东西{\r}\Nhe always made me feel like I was something evil.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.30,1:03:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 看看我现在 - 我觉得年轻了几岁{\r}\N- And look at me now. - I feel years younger.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:36.23,1:03:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你知道,多一个像这样的今天 我们将一脸土灰{\r}\NYou know, one more like this one today, and we'll be naturally gray.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.40,1:03:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这是一个令人难以置信的工作 我真的认为这超过100万{\r}\NIt was an incredible job. I really think it's won'th more than a million.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.74,1:03:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}抱歉,亲爱的,但我可不想回去 重写我的赎金纸条{\r}\NI'm sorry, darling, but I'm not going back...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.44,1:03:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那将背离了我的祈祷书{\r}\Nand rewrite my ransom note that I left in my prayer book.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.25,1:03:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你必须好好动一动 去解决这100万{\r}\NYou'll have to be a good sport and settle for a million.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.28,1:03:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你很漂亮,法兰,很漂亮{\r}\NYou were beautiful, Fran. Just beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.99,1:03:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我很害怕 - 我告诉过你没问题的,不是吗?{\r}\N- I was scared. - I told you it'd be all right, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.79,1:04:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}人们在教堂是很守礼节的{\r}\NPeople in church are inibited.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.56,1:04:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他们不会跳起来乱跑 或是制造噪音,他们都虔诚有礼{\r}\NThey don't jump up and run around and make a lot of noise.\NThey're all too religiously polite.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.10,1:04:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们要继续自我陶醉 或是你想谈谈他呢?{\r}\NShall we go on congratulating ourselves,\Nor would you like to talk about him now?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.97,1:04:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 谁? - 谁?{\r}\N- Who? - "Who."
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.70,1:04:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那个叼着烟斗的男人{\r}\NThe man with the pipe.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.41,1:04:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你看到他在那里? - 如影随形{\r}\N- So you saw him there, huh? - Larger than life.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.68,1:04:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}比死亡还难缠{\r}\NLarger than death, you mean.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.68,1:04:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他现在追求的毫无疑问了{\r}\NThere's no doubt about who he's after now.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.98,1:04:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你打算怎么处理他,亲爱的{\r}\NWhat were you planning to do about him, dear,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.28,1:04:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}除了不想告诉我的以外?{\r}\Nbesides just not telling me?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.52,1:04:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不打算对他做任何事情{\r}\NI'm not planning to do anything about him.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.06,1:04:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}乔森・马洛尼渴望的那份工作 现在他得到了{\r}\NJoe Maloney's been itching for that job. He's got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.63,1:04:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我会打电话给他 等我把我们的客人安置好后{\r}\NI'll phone him as soon as we put our guest in his quarters.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.30,1:04:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我说得对,那计程车司机真傻{\r}\NI was right about that silly cab driver.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.73,1:04:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}在我的生命里 这次我讨厌说对了{\r}\NFor once in my life I hate being right.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.34,1:04:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他怎么会知道我们要去那里 除了你和我,世上还有谁会知道?{\r}\NWell, how in the hell could he have known we were going to be there...\Nwhen you and I are the only two people in the world who knew that?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.21,1:04:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我有一个想法{\r}\N[Sighs] I've got a thought.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.21,1:04:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 就是有点愚蠢 - 说吧{\r}\N- It's a dumb one. - Say it.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.88,1:04:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你相信特异功能吗?{\r}\NDo you believe in E.S.P.?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.01,1:05:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}特异功能,超常的心灵现象{\r}\NExtra sensory perception, all that psychic phenomena?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.42,1:05:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}什么意思? 是说那个叫什么的夫人?{\r}\NWhat do you mean? Madame What's-her-name?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.32,1:05:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}布兰琪・泰勒{\r}\NBlanche Tyler.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.82,1:05:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}老天{\r}\NJesus.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.09,1:05:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你和我都知道这一面墙 但我们能犯错吗?{\r}\NYou and I know that that's off the wall, but, uh, can we afford to be wrong?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.90,1:05:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}恐怕我们的那对欢喜冤家 将会共同发生一起致命的事故{\r}\NI'm afraid our two quarrelsome lovers are going to have to share a fatal accident.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:20.04,1:05:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}噢,我的天啊{\r}\NOh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.41,1:05:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但马洛尼不会这么做的,对吧?{\r}\NBut Maloney wouldn't be willing to do that, would he?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.78,1:05:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}当然,他会很乐意做的{\r}\NOf course he'd be willing. Gladly.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.55,1:05:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他会相信那是为了保护自己 和他的老伙伴{\r}\NHe'd believe he was protecting himself and his old buddy.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.55,1:05:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不想知道,好吗?{\r}\NI don't want to know about it. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.55,1:05:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 答应我,亚瑟 - 拜托,亲爱的{\r}\N- Promise me, Arthur. - Come on, now, dear.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.76,1:05:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这有什么好激动的{\r}\NThat's what's so exciting about all of this.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.13,1:05:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们同生共死 没有什么好退缩的{\r}\NWe move as one. Everything together. Nothing held back.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.13,1:06:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这是严重的疏失,就这样失去他 他是我们的所有{\r}\NIt was gross negligence, losing him that way. He was all we had.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.13,1:06:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我没有失去他,他只是被绑架{\r}\NI didn't lose him. He was kidnapped.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.97,1:06:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}为什么会有人对主教干这种事?{\r}\NWhy would anyone want to do that to a bishop?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.74,1:06:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}为了赎金啊,傻瓜 那可是100万美元{\r}\NFor the ransom, dummy. It's a million dollars.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.28,1:06:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我无能为力,你知道,我就在那儿{\r}\NI can't get over it. You know, I was right there.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.92,1:06:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}噢,忘了那100万吧 我们的一万该怎么办?{\r}\NTsk. Oh, forget about the million. What about out 10,000?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.83,1:06:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们现在无路可走,鲁尼{\r}\NWe've got nowhere to go now, Lumley.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.20,1:06:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我该怎么告诉兰伯特女士?{\r}\NWhat am I gonna tell Miss Rainbird?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.40,1:07:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}看来我和亨利又得费尽心力 来补原本该是你的工作{\r}\NI suppose Henry and I are going to have to exhaust ourselves again doing your work for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.04,1:07:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}什么意思,我的工作? 我的工作是驾驶该死的计程车{\r}\NWhat d'ya mean, my work? My work is driving a goddamn cab,\Nfor Christ's sake.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.57,1:07:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}看在上帝的分上 从这一分钟开始,做点正确的…{\r}\NAnd startir right this minute, that's exact... [Phone Ringing]
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.04,1:07:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 正确的什么? 继续说 - 接电话{\r}\N- That's exact what? Go ahead. - Answer the telephone.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.12,1:07:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}哈罗? 谁?{\r}\NHello? Who?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.59,1:07:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}马洛尼先生?{\r}\NMr. Maloney?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.72,1:07:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}巴洛溪? 请继续{\r}\NBarlow Creek? Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.93,1:07:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}哈罗{\r}\NHello.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.06,1:07:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你能说大声一点吗? 马洛尼先生{\r}\NCan you speak a little louder, Mr. Maloney?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.70,1:07:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我说我透过你那律师朋友 驾驶的车牌号码追查到你{\r}\NI said I traced you through the license plates on that car your lawyer friend was driving.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.24,1:07:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我猜你仍然想寻找艾迪・休奎奇{\r}\NI figured if you was still lookir for some dope on Eddie Shoebridge,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.34,1:07:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我可以给你一点情报 - 哦{\r}\N- I might have somethir for you. - Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.84,1:07:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你为什么改变主意了 马洛尼先生?{\r}\NHow come you changed your mind, Mr. Maloney?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.61,1:07:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我没和你的人说 是因为我觉得不关我的事{\r}\NI didn't say nothir to your man 'cause I felt it was none of my business and none of his,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.82,1:07:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但我一直在想 我可以因此赚点外快{\r}\Nbut I been thinkir about it and how I could use the bread.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.32,1:07:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}因此考虑过后 我愿意带你去见一个人{\r}\NSo for a little consideration, I'm willing to lead you to someone...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.02,1:07:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他认识艾迪・休奎奇的太太{\r}\Nwho knows Eddie Shoebridge's wife.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:54.16,1:07:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你得付一大笔钱{\r}\NIt'll cost you a grand. [Laughs]
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.13,1:07:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}喔,别傻了,马洛尼先生{\r}\NOh, don't be silly, Mr. Maloney.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.86,1:08:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我的律师就在我的身边{\r}\NI have my lawyer right here beside me,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.07,1:08:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他说愿意付你100美元 只要能找到人{\r}\Nand he says he'll give you $100 provided it leads to something.\NMake it two.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:08.84,1:08:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}喔,好吧,成交{\r}\NOh... All right. It's a deal.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.41,1:08:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我们在哪碰面? - 你和你的律师朋友…{\r}\N- Where do we meet? - You and that lawyer friend of yours,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.94,1:08:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你们开车来 两个小时后在梅布斯见面{\r}\Nyou drive up and meet me at Abe and Mabel's in two hours.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.75,1:08:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 梅布斯? - 是路边咖啡屋,在榭尔曼路上{\r}\N- Abe and Mabel's? - It's a cafe up the road to Mt. Sherman,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.59,1:08:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}进入22号公路后大约五英哩 你知道哪里吗?{\r}\Nabout five miles off Route 22.\N- You know where it is? - Yeah. Why so far away?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.49,1:08:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}知道,为什么到那么远? 我们不能找个更方便的地方吗?{\r}\NCan't we meet somewhere more convenient?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.99,1:08:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我要带你去的派对就在那边{\r}\NThis party I'm gonna take you to happens to be up in that area.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:33.66,1:08:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我明白了,马洛尼先生 你肯定艾迪・休奎奇还活着?{\r}\NI see. Mr. Maloney, are you admitting Edward Shoebridge is still alive?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.83,1:08:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}两个小时后 我看到白花花的钞票再说{\r}\NI ain't sayir a thing till I see the color of your money, in two hours.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:44.64,1:08:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你怎么想? - 我闻到鱼腥味{\r}\N- What d'ya think? - Smells fishy to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.78,1:08:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我知道{\r}\NI know.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:48.78,1:08:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但是当你快饿死时 甚至鱼腥味都会觉得好{\r}\NBut even fish smells good when you're starving to death.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.48,1:08:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们会有什么损失? 他是唯一的线索{\r}\NWhat have we got to lose? He's the only clue left.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.35,1:08:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你有200美元吗?{\r}\NYou got $200 on you?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.06,1:09:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你比我更清楚{\r}\NYou know me better than that.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.06,1:09:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}当然没有,再给我一个{\r}\NOf course not. Fix me another one of these.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.23,1:09:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你不需要,你已经有一个了 我们只有两个小时去那里{\r}\NYou don't need another one. You already got one. We only got two hours to get there.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.63,1:09:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我要在车上吃 - 走吧{\r}\N- I'll eat it in the car. - Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.80,1:09:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你真难应付{\r}\NYou're impossible.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.23,1:10:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}两杯啤酒,麻烦{\r}\NA couple of beers, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.74,1:10:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他迟到了{\r}\NHe must be late.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.30,1:11:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}谢谢{\r}\NThank you, dear. [Car Approaching, Brakes Squeal]
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.78,1:11:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}孩子们,去坐那边{\r}\NYou kids sit over there.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.59,1:11:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 哦,今天周日的学校如何? - 吵死了{\r}\NHow was Sunday school today? Noisy.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.03,1:11:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 五瓶可乐,麻烦 - 我们没有吵啊{\r}\N- Five Cokes, please. - We didn't make any noise.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.79,1:11:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这就对了,所以你才在这里{\r}\NThat's right. That's why you're here.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.36,1:12:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不要怪我{\r}\NDon't blame me.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.59,1:12:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我有说什么吗?{\r}\NDid I say anything? [Door Opens, Closes]
Dialogue: 0,1:12:31.27,1:12:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你好,抱歉,我迟到了 - 我帮你搬张椅子{\r}\N- Hello. I'm sorry I'm late. - I'll get you a chair.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.00,1:12:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 没关系,我坐这儿 - 我和你坐一起{\r}\NThat's all right. I'll sit over here. I'll join you.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.35,1:12:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}瞧,好手段{\r}\NLook at that. Nice arrangement.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:48.35,1:12:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}别下流了,乔治{\r}\NDon't be obscene, George.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.36,1:13:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}喔{\r}\NOh.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:01.40,1:13:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}谢谢,亲爱的{\r}\NThank you, my dear.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:08.37,1:13:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}让头脑保持清醒,好吗?{\r}\NJust see that you keep you head screwed on straight, will you?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:23.65,1:13:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他不会来了{\r}\NHe's not coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:41.26,1:14:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}噢,就这样结束了{\r}\NWell, that's the end of that.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:55.75,1:14:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}乔治,在急什么?{\r}\NGeorge, what's the big hurry?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.15,1:15:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}开慢一点,好吗?{\r}\NJust slow down a little, will ya, please?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.36,1:15:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我说了别开那么快,乔治!{\r}\NI told you not to drive so fast, George!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:11.33,1:15:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不知道怎么回事 油门好像卡住了{\r}\NI don't know what's wrong. The accelerator seems to be sticking.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.00,1:15:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}乔治,看在老天的份上 开慢点,好吗?{\r}\NGeorge, for God's sake, slow up, will ya?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.17,1:15:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我做不到{\r}\N[Tires Screeching] I can't.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.24,1:15:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我的汉堡快要吐出来了{\r}\NMy hamburger's coming up.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:23.67,1:15:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}油门…卡住了{\r}\NThe accelerator... is stuck.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:26.61,1:15:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}踩煞车!{\r}\NUse the brakes!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.31,1:15:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 没反应 - 什么?{\r}\N- They don't work. - What?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:34.62,1:15:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 煞车没反应 - 什么意思?{\r}\N- The brakes don't work. - What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:42.56,1:15:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 乔治 - 拜托,别抓我,看在老天的份上!{\r}\N- George! - Come on, woman. Don't grab me, for God's sake!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:45.93,1:15:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不是我,是煞车坏了{\r}\NIt's not me. It's the brakes don't work.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:48.10,1:15:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我快得心脏病了,乔治{\r}\NI'm getting violently ill, George.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.90,1:15:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你快让我窒息了,布兰琪,老天 - 乔治{\r}\N- You're chokir me, Blanche, for Christ's sake! - George!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:55.74,1:15:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}快想办法!{\r}\NDo something!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:05.48,1:16:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}拉手煞车! 伸手拉手煞车!{\r}\NGrab the brake! Reach down and pull the hand brake.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:09.15,1:16:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 快拉 - 我在拉了!{\r}\N- Pull on it! - I am pulling!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:11.25,1:16:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你的手别抓方向盘,快拉!{\r}\NGet your hands off the steering wheel. Pull on it!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.42,1:16:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我在拉了 - 快拉{\r}\N- I am pulling. - Pull it.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.66,1:16:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}快啊{\r}\NCome on.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:21.16,1:16:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你的手别抓方向盘,该死的!{\r}\NGet your hand off the goddamn wheel!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.14,1:17:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我得离开这条路{\r}\N- [Horns Honking] - I gotta get off this road.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.55,1:17:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}布兰琪,坚持住{\r}\NBlanche, just hang on.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:28.82,1:18:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}有趣吗?{\r}\NWasrt that fun?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:31.19,1:18:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 去你的,乔治・鲁尼 - 你吃错药啦?{\r}\N- Damn you, George Lumley! - What's the matter with you?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:34.53,1:18:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 不是我,是马洛尼 - 开车的不是他!{\r}\NIt wasrt me. It's Maloney. He wasrt driving!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:37.30,1:18:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那当然,是他对车动了手脚 弄坏了煞车{\r}\NOf course, but he screwed up the car and broke the brakes.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:40.34,1:18:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 马洛尼? - 没错{\r}\N- Maloney? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.71,1:18:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你认为这是巧合,布兰琪?{\r}\NYou think it's a coincidence, Blanche?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:45.91,1:18:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}嗯?{\r}\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.15,1:18:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你的车…可能要大修几天了{\r}\NYour car... is gonna be out of commission for a couple days.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:54.08,1:18:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们想个办法回家吧{\r}\NSo let's go find us another way to get home.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:59.46,1:19:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}乔治,你没事吧?{\r}\NGeorge. Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:02.93,1:19:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}嗯,我想是吧,你呢?{\r}\NMm-hmm. I think so. How about you?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.70,1:19:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我很好,对不起{\r}\NI'm okay. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:12.74,1:19:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你真的认为马洛尼要我们死? - 嗯哼{\r}\N- Do you really think Maloney wanted us dead? - Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.94,1:19:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}为什么? 老天 为何有人会想这样对我们?{\r}\NWhy, in the name of God, would anyone want to do that to us?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.18,1:19:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不知道{\r}\NI don't know,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:24.18,1:19:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但可以打赌,肯定和你那个 神秘的朋友艾迪・休奎奇有关{\r}\Nbut you can bet is has something to do with your mysterious friend, Eddie Shoebridge.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:28.22,1:19:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}或许马洛尼就把他埋在他家后院{\r}\NMaloney's probably got him buried in his backyard.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.99,1:19:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不希望被我们给找到{\r}\NDoesrt want us to find out.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.48,1:20:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那边{\r}\NThat way.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:41.99,1:20:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你好,抱歉,迟到了{\r}\NHi there. Sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.99,1:20:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}恭喜你对我们的车干的好事 做得很完美,马洛尼{\r}\NCongratulations on the nice job you did on our car, Maloney.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.76,1:20:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}为什么你们俩要站在路中间?{\r}\NWhat are you two doir standir in the middle of the road?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:50.97,1:20:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你明知我们为何站在路上 马洛尼{\r}\NYou know perfectly well what we're doing on the road, Maloney.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:54.04,1:20:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你一定就是布兰琪・泰勒 很高兴见到你,你的车子呢?{\r}\NYou must be Blanche Tyler. Pleased to meet ya. Where's your car?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:57.57,1:21:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这么说吧,它不太听话 你明白我的意思吧?{\r}\NLet's just say it ain't in runnir order, you know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:00.68,1:21:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}上车,我载你们到最近的车站{\r}\NHop in. I'll give ya a lift to the nearest station.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.88,1:21:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不,谢了,我们不坐灵车{\r}\NNo, thank you. We don't ride in hearses.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:07.45,1:21:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你以为我是来这里玩的?{\r}\NYou think I came up here for the fun of it?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:09.45,1:21:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是你要我带你去派对 那人认识艾迪・休奎奇的太太啊{\r}\NThen you want me to take you to this party that knows Eddie Shoebridge's wife.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:12.12,1:21:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你为什么不继续前进,自己走吧 马洛尼,我们当没看到{\r}\NWhy don't you just go ahead, uh, by yourself this time, Maloney. We'll skip it.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:27.70,1:21:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他真是迷人{\r}\NHe's all charm.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.22,1:22:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那是谁?{\r}\N[Blanche] Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:16.69,1:22:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是马洛尼,他跟着我们{\r}\NThat's Maloney. He's after us.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:19.52,1:22:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}快点{\r}\NCome on.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.27,1:22:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}嘿,伙计们,我们快闪{\r}\N[Man] Hey, guys, let's get the hell outta here.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:03.13,1:23:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们最好通知警察{\r}\NWe better get the police.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:07.67,1:23:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}然后损失我们的一万美元?{\r}\NAnd lose our $10,000?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.50,1:23:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我能帮你吗? 夫人{\r}\NMay I be of some help to you, madam?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:40.00,1:23:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我想看一些手镯 - 要特定款式吗?{\r}\N- I'd like to see some bracelets. - Any particular kind?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.24,1:23:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你有绿宝石或珍珠的吗?{\r}\NDo you have anything with turquoise, or perhaps pearls?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:55.98,1:23:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我们的客人还好吗? - 他很好{\r}\N- Anything wrong with our houseguest? - He's fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:58.92,1:24:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我给了他一顿丰盛的午餐 和一瓶新产的红酒{\r}\NI gave him a very nice lunch and a fresh bottle of wine.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:03.49,1:24:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 或许这其中一条会吸引你? - 这些是海洋珍珠?{\r}\N- Maybe one of these will appeal to you? - Are those seed pearls?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:07.43,1:24:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是的{\r}\NThat's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:12.77,1:24:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你来这里干嘛? - 这些看起来像淡水珍珠{\r}\N- What are you doing here? - These look like freshwater pearls.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.24,1:24:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}有消息传来{\r}\NThe message has come through on KFAG.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:20.71,1:24:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他们已经准备好 我们所提出的宝石了{\r}\NThey've located the stone we asked for.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:23.51,1:24:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}在纽约温士顿{\r}\NIn New York. Harry Winston.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:25.88,1:24:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}53克拉{\r}\NFifty-three carats.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:30.35,1:24:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这些都很好,多少钱?{\r}\NThese are very nice. How much are they?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.99,1:24:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}315美元,含税{\r}\N$315, including tax.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.93,1:24:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们什么时候行动?{\r}\NWhen do we make the pickup?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:40.53,1:24:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}明晚9:30{\r}\NTomorrow night, 9:30.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.37,1:24:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好的,现在回家吧{\r}\NGood. Now go on home.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:46.77,1:24:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你能不能把这些先预留下来{\r}\NWould it be possible for you to set these aside...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:49.67,1:24:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}以便我可以带丈夫过来看看?{\r}\Nso that I can bring in my husband and he can look at them?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:51.94,1:24:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}当然可以,夫人{\r}\NOf course, madam.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:53.94,1:24:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}还有一个坏消息{\r}\N[Sighs] Now for the bad news.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:57.71,1:24:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}看看这个{\r}\NTake a look at this.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:59.55,1:25:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}(男子死于公路离奇事故){\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.20,1:25:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}没用的废物,他搞砸了{\r}\NIncompetent bastard. He blew it.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.43,1:25:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}现在我们得自己去干掉他们{\r}\NNow we'll have to eliminate these two ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.20,1:25:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我们? - 没错{\r}\N- Ourselves? - That's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.54,1:25:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}明晚,等我们把客人送走后{\r}\NTomorrow night, right after we return our guest.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:29.81,1:25:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我不行 - 你必须做{\r}\N- I can't. - You must.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:34.42,1:25:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}记着,共谋等同于主谋{\r}\NRemember: Share and share alike.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.82,1:25:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你别说了! 别说了!{\r}\NYou stop it! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:47.00,1:25:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 决定了吗? - 这个好{\r}\N- Decide on something? - That'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:49.87,1:25:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我要这一个{\r}\NI'll have it wrapped.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:52.00,1:25:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但不仅如此,远远不止于此{\r}\N[Man] But it was more than that, much more than that...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:55.74,1:25:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你留下了生命中珍贵的礼物{\r}\Nthat you left behind as your precious gift to life.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:59.78,1:26:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是的,乔森・马洛尼 你是一个慷慨的人{\r}\NYes, Joseph Maloney, you were a generous man.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:04.45,1:26:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你献出了你的心和灵魂{\r}\NYou gave of your heart and soul.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:06.95,1:26:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你献出了最好的你{\r}\NYou gave the very best that was in you,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:09.58,1:26:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}凡世上无人比你付出的更多{\r}\Nand no more than that can be asked of mortal man on this earth.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:13.76,1:26:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你深爱你的妻子{\r}\NYou loved your wife dearly.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:16.63,1:26:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你给予你亲爱的母亲和父亲{\r}\NYou bestowed upon your dear mother and father...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:19.70,1:26:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}所有的照料,所有的关心{\r}\Nall the care, all the attention,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.43,1:26:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}在他们的晚年 给予他们需要的耐心和安慰{\r}\Npatience and comfort that they needed...\Nin the sunset of their lives.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:28.97,1:26:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们这些留下的人们{\r}\NAnd those of us who are left behind...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:31.51,1:26:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}为你而哀伤,乔森{\r}\Nto grieve for you, Joseph,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:34.04,1:26:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}只能遵从上帝的决定{\r}\Ncan only bow to the divine judgement of our Lord,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:38.01,1:26:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}谁选择了带你远离我们{\r}\Nwho has chosen to take you away from us...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:41.62,1:26:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}在一场残酷的意外{\r}\Nin this cruel accident.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:45.22,1:26:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}喔,神圣伟大的主啊{\r}\NOh, how great the holiness of our God.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:48.82,1:26:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}k拥有一切智慧{\r}\NFor He knoweth all things.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:51.79,1:26:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}k无所不知{\r}\NAnd there is not anything save He knows it.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:55.60,1:26:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}k来到了这个世界{\r}\NAnd He cometh into the world...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:58.50,1:27:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}k可以拯救世人 如果他们能去倾听k的声音{\r}\Nthat He may save all men if they will harken unto His voice.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:04.31,1:27:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}因为k看到了世人遭受的痛苦{\r}\NFor behold, He suffered that the pains of all men.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.41,1:27:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是的,每一个活着的生命 都在遭受痛苦{\r}\NYea, the pains of every living creature,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:12.28,1:27:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}男人、女人和孩童…{\r}\Nboth men, women and children...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.96,1:27:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你就不能让我独自一人吗?{\r}\NCan't you leave me alone?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:31.40,1:27:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你杀了他还不够吗?{\r}\NIsn't it enough that you killed him?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:33.74,1:27:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}并非如此,马洛尼太太 事情正好相反{\r}\NThat's not so, Mrs. Maloney. It was the other way.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:37.44,1:27:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是你,是你来这里之后 开始了一切{\r}\NYou. You started it all coming here...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.44,1:27:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}并且在你那交易中 把事情搞得一团糟{\r}\Nand messing in things that were none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:43.15,1:27:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}请走开,拜托{\r}\NNow go away. Please!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:45.75,1:27:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 马洛尼太太,我要和你谈谈 - 他已经死了,埋葬了{\r}\N- Mrs. Maloney, I have to talk to you. - He's dead and buried.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.25,1:27:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 没有什么可谈的 - 他为什么不想要我…{\r}\N- There's nothing to talk about. - Why didn't he want me...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:50.39,1:27:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 寻找艾迪・休奎奇? - 我不想听你说话{\r}\N- Iooking for Eddie Shoebridge? - I am not listening to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:53.16,1:27:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 离开我! - 马洛尼太太,你丈夫要杀我{\r}\N- Get away from me! - Mrs. Maloney, your husband tried to kill me,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:55.82,1:27:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你也有份,是吗? - 不{\r}\N- and you were in on it, werert you? - No.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:58.03,1:28:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 那为何总是逃避我? 那就是原因? - 不{\r}\N- Then why are you always running away from me? Is that why? - No.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:01.93,1:28:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你知道你是企图谋杀的共犯吗?{\r}\NDo you realize that you are an accessory to an attempted murder?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:05.67,1:28:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 与我无关 - 也许警方会认为你也有份{\r}\N- I had nothing to do with that. - Perhaps the police would think that you did.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:10.11,1:28:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你要我去跟警察说吗? - 看在老天的份上{\r}\N- You want me to go to the police about it? - For God's sake.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:13.94,1:28:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你不会那样… - 告诉我艾迪・休奎奇在哪儿?{\r}\N- You wouldn't do that... - Just tell me where is Eddie Shoebridge?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:18.91,1:28:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我不能 - 马洛尼太太,他在哪? 请告诉我{\r}\NI can't. Mrs. Maloney, where is he? Please tell me.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:25.92,1:28:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}没有艾迪・休奎奇{\r}\NThere is no Eddie Shoebridge.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:29.83,1:28:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他如烟雾般25年前来到这都市{\r}\NHe went up in smoke 25 years ago and came down in the city.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:34.96,1:28:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他自称亚瑟・亚当森{\r}\NHe calls himself Arthur Adamson.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:39.30,1:28:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}亚瑟・亚当森?{\r}\NArthur Adamson?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:44.14,1:28:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如果他发现我告诉了你 他会杀了我{\r}\NIf he finds out I told you, he'll kill me.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:46.98,1:28:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}走开吧,别再靠近我了{\r}\NNow go away, and don't ever come near me again.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:54.85,1:28:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}骗子! 骗子!{\r}\NFake! Fake! [Sobbing]
Dialogue: 0,1:29:07.55,1:29:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}(艾迪・休奎奇){\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:11.73,1:29:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}等等,你这是在夸大{\r}\NWait a second, now. You're the one that's exaggerating.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:14.77,1:29:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不,不,我是失踪了两三天 但不可能更多了{\r}\NNo, I'll give you two or three days maybe I missed, but never more than that.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:18.51,1:29:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 告诉他这非常重要 - 嘘{\r}\N- Tell him it's deeply important. - Shh!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:21.88,1:29:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 硬起来 - 为何是我?{\r}\N- Stand up. - Why me?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:24.48,1:29:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是什么使你认为是我跑超过里程?{\r}\NWhat makes you think that it's me that ran up all the extra mileage?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:27.65,1:29:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那些家伙如何,贺比或艾尔 值日班的人{\r}\NWhat about that little asshole, Herbie, or, uh, Al, the one on the day shift?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:32.95,1:29:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我明白了,我会去的{\r}\NI understand. I'll be there.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.56,1:29:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是,我保证我会过去{\r}\NYes, I promise I'll be there.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:42.53,1:29:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}答案是不行{\r}\NThe answer's no.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.57,1:29:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他说我必须轮班 并且我今晚就要上工{\r}\NHe says I must work the shift, and I must work it tonight.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:48.14,1:29:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}帮我个忙,布兰琪{\r}\NAnd do me a favor, Blanche.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:50.44,1:29:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}拜托别再给我制造麻烦{\r}\NPlease don't give me a hard time.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:52.87,1:29:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你没有全力去抗争{\r}\NYou didn't put up much of a fight.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:54.98,1:29:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}亲爱的,听着 我一直消磨时间在帮你{\r}\NHoney, look. After all the goofir off I've been doir on your behalf,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:58.78,1:30:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我差点就要失去我的驾驶座 被踢出公司了{\r}\NI'm within a gnat's eyelash of losir my cab and gettir kicked right out of the company.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:03.65,1:30:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}鲁尼,你真傻! 你不需要开计程车{\r}\NLumley, you're thick! You won't have to drive a cab...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:06.49,1:30:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如果你能把这件事办好 就能拿到钱啊{\r}\Nif you can get this thing over and done with and collect the money.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.56,1:30:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}"如果",亲爱的 你总是对我说如果{\r}\N"If," darling. You're always givir me ifs.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:11.96,1:30:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不能靠如果吃饭,你也不能{\r}\NI can't eat ifs and neither can you,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:13.96,1:30:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}朱莉亚・兰伯特和你之间的 华尔滋太过遥远了{\r}\Nwhile Julia Rainbird and you are waltzir around in the great beyond.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:17.13,1:30:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}拜托,亲爱的 我该做的就是回去工作{\r}\NCome on, sweetheart. The least I can do is show up for work every now and then.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:20.37,1:30:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}至少,我不是已经给你 那家伙的名字了吗?{\r}\NAfter all, didn't I give you the guy's name?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:22.64,1:30:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但是电话簿里满满的都是 亚瑟・亚当森{\r}\NBut the phone book is full of Arthur Adamsons.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:24.94,1:30:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这很简单,你要做的 就是找出正确的那一个{\r}\NIt's very simple. All you need to do is find out the right one.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:28.84,1:30:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那很容易,一个大约40岁{\r}\NThat's a snap. The one that's close to 40 years old...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:31.81,1:30:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}听到艾迪・休奎奇这名字 就会颤抖的家伙{\r}\Nand trembles a little bit at the name Eddie Shoebridge.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:33.92,1:30:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 简单,我们明天来做 - 现在做会更好{\r}\N- Easy. We do that tomorrow. - Now would be much better.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:36.99,1:30:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}食物就要到手了,鲁尼 拜托你,亲爱的{\r}\NA bird in the hand, Lumley. Please. Oh, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:40.09,1:30:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}唯一的食物是在我的手上{\r}\NThe only bird that's gonna be in my hand...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:42.29,1:30:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我必须遗憾地说{\r}\Nand I'm very sorry to say this...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:44.36,1:30:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}四点至午夜我必须开车{\r}\Nis a steering wheel from 4:00 to midnight.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:48.23,1:30:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好吧,我何时才能得到一个吻?{\r}\NSure. Why should I get a kiss?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:51.20,1:30:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}当我开始认为 你不再难以忍受的时候{\r}\NJust when I was beginning to think you werert impossible.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:53.80,1:30:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}也许没有你我也能做到{\r}\NMaybe I'll do it without you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:55.80,1:30:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}绝不可能!{\r}\NThe hell you will!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:57.94,1:30:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}来吧,布兰琪,拜托{\r}\NCome on, now. Please.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:59.94,1:31:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这个休奎奇惹了许多麻烦 不想被发现{\r}\NThis Shoebridge fellow's gone to a lot of trouble not to be found.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:03.14,1:31:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如今你不知道会被卷入 什么麻烦当中{\r}\NNow you got no idea what kind of trouble you could get into.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:06.51,1:31:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不管是什么,他会忘了那些事的{\r}\NWhatever it is, he'll forget about it...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:09.08,1:31:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}当他听到他将获得数百万时{\r}\Nwhen he hears about the millions he's coming into.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:11.55,1:31:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}噢,布兰琪,拜托{\r}\NOh, Blanche, come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:13.76,1:31:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}坐下吧,你漂亮的小…屁股{\r}\NJust sit down on your pretty little... behind.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:18.16,1:31:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我得说,这很…{\r}\NAnd I must say, it is quite an...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:20.56,1:31:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不,这是很吸引人的小屁股{\r}\NNo, it is. Very attractive little behind.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:23.10,1:31:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}等我,好吗?{\r}\NJust wait for me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:25.27,1:31:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}今晚我回到家,我们会…{\r}\NAnd tonight when I get home, we will, uh...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:29.97,1:31:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}很好,好好地商量我们的策略{\r}\NRight. Very nice. Plot our strategy.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:33.51,1:31:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}明白我的意思吗? 亲爱的{\r}\NKnow what I mean, darlir?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:50.99,1:31:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}谁需要他{\r}\NWho needs him.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:59.25,1:32:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}(亚当森医生){\r}\N[Buzzer Buzzing]
Dialogue: 0,1:32:03.87,1:32:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你不会是亚瑟・亚当森,对吧?{\r}\NYou wouldn't be Arthur Adamson, would you?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:07.01,1:32:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}抱歉{\r}\NExcuse me.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:10.75,1:32:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}(亚当森空调){\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:14.42,1:32:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}抱歉!{\r}\NExcuse me!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:19.19,1:32:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}哈罗,你是亚瑟・亚当森?{\r}\NHello. Are you Arthur Adamson?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:22.22,1:32:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}嘿,亚瑟!{\r}\NHey, Art!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:25.99,1:32:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}什么事?{\r}\NYeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:29.25,1:32:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}(亚当森车厂){\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:33.25,1:32:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}(A.A.亚当森管理员){\r}\N[Doorbell Ringing]
Dialogue: 0,1:32:49.75,1:32:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}(亚当森珠宝){\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:53.19,1:32:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}对不起,我们打烊了{\r}\NI'm sorry. We're just closing.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:55.19,1:32:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我知道,我不是要购物 请问亚当森先生在吗?{\r}\NI understand. I'm not shopping. Is Mr. Adamson around?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:59.66,1:33:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 不,他不在,但你可以明天再来 - 好的{\r}\NI'm afraid not. But if you come back tomorrow...\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:04.43,1:33:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但是为了确认是我要找的 亚当森先生{\r}\NBut just to be sure I have the right Mr. Adamson,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:07.04,1:33:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我猜他是一位年约40岁的绅士? - 是的,没错{\r}\N- he is a gentleman of about 40, I trust? - Yes, that's about right.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.67,1:33:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}噢,整个下午以来 这是第一个令人鼓舞的消息{\r}\NOh, that's the first encouraging news I've had all afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:14.84,1:33:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}为了不耽误时间 我到哪里能找到他?{\r}\NIsn't there someplace I might reach him without delay?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:17.71,1:33:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你是说今晚? - 是的{\r}\N- You mean tonight? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:19.71,1:33:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他平常都会直接从这里回家{\r}\NWell, he usually goes directly home from here.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:23.02,1:33:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但今晚很不幸 因为我想他今天要开个派对{\r}\NBut tonight would be very bad because I believe he's giving a party.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:26.55,1:33:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我知道他今天提早离开 是为了这个原因{\r}\NI know he left unusually early for some such reason.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:29.79,1:33:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是不是有什么我可以帮你转达的 在明天早上?{\r}\NIsn't there something I can tell him for you in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:32.49,1:33:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 这是私人事情,相当私人 - 喔,我明白了{\r}\N- This is personal. Rather personal. - Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:36.13,1:33:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}或是你想留个字条给他{\r}\NPerhaps you'd like to leave him a note.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:39.53,1:33:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 字条? 是的 - 好的,请这边走{\r}\N- A note? Very good. - Yes. Come this way.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:43.77,1:33:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}抱歉{\r}\NExcuse me.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:48.04,1:33:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}谢谢{\r}\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:03.29,1:34:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}有什么问题吗?{\r}\NIs anything the matter?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:05.73,1:34:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}嗯,我只是在想…{\r}\NUh, I was, uh, just thinking.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:08.33,1:34:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}与其留字条在这里{\r}\NInstead of leaving this note here,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:11.20,1:34:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不如这样会更好,我今晚 就发个电报给亚当森先生{\r}\Nit might be better if I sent Mr. Adamson a telegram tonight.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:15.44,1:34:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 能告诉我他的地址吗? - 呃,我不能…{\r}\N- What's his address, please? - Well, I don't...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:18.67,1:34:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}没关系的,我们是朋友{\r}\NIt's all right. We're friends.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:22.11,1:34:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 富兰克林街1001号 - 富兰克林街1001号{\r}\N- 1001 Franklin Street. - 1001 Franklin.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:24.68,1:34:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}非常感谢你,你真是亲切{\r}\NThank you very much. You've been very kind.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:30.49,1:34:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你是摩羯座的吗?{\r}\NYou're a Capricorn, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:32.69,1:34:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不,我是狮子座{\r}\NNo, I'm a Leo.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:35.96,1:34:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我想也是{\r}\NThat's what I thought.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:54.38,1:34:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 皮特,嗨 - 哈罗,布兰琪宝贝{\r}\N- Pete, hi. - Hello, there, Blanche, baby.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:56.44,1:35:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你有看到乔治吗? - 他几分钟前刚离开,很快会回来{\r}\N- Have you seen George? - He just left a few minutes ago, but he'll be back.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:00.38,1:35:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}送四个人到河谷参加派对{\r}\NTook a party of four out to River Valley.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:02.85,1:35:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 喔,亲爱的,那可能要通宵 - 放轻松,有什么事吗?{\r}\N- Oh, dear. That could take all night. - Easily. What's up?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:05.95,1:35:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你能帮我传个话给他吗? - 当然可以{\r}\N- Would you give him a message for me? - Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:08.29,1:35:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 告诉他说我找到他了 - 你找到他?{\r}\N- Just tell him I found him. - You found him?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:10.93,1:35:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 没错,他住在富兰克林1001号 - 富兰克林1001号{\r}\N- That's right. He lives at 1001 Franklin. - 1001 Franklin.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:15.16,1:35:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那就是他的住所 而我现在就要过去{\r}\NThat's where he lives, and that's where I'm going now.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:17.70,1:35:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你找到他了,那就是他的住所 并且你现在就要过去{\r}\NYou found him, and that's where he lives, and that's where you're going now.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:20.44,1:35:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 谢谢,皮特 - 随时候劳,布兰琪{\r}\N- Thanks, Pete. - Any time, Blanche.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:32.35,1:35:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你要去踩点了?{\r}\NYou wanna go over the new pickup spot once again?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:35.15,1:35:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我记在心里{\r}\NI know it by heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:37.42,1:35:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你没问题吧?{\r}\NAre you all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:40.82,1:35:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我没问题 - 你确定?{\r}\N- I will be. - You sure?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:47.10,1:35:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}必须在9:30前到达,我们走吧{\r}\NHave to be there at 9:30. Let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:28.60,1:36:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}伍德主教,该走了{\r}\NBishop Wood, it's time to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:31.04,1:36:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你有穿上你的法衣吗?{\r}\NHave you your vestments on?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:33.27,1:36:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是的,但我还没吃完鸡{\r}\NYes, but I haven't finished the chicken.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:38.45,1:36:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}对不起,阁下{\r}\NI'm sorry, Your Excellency.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:41.55,1:36:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我要你照以下说的做{\r}\NHere's what I want you to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:43.75,1:36:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}请把椅子放在房间中央{\r}\NPlace the armchair in the center of the room...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:46.09,1:36:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}背对着门,坐在椅子上{\r}\Nfacing away from the door and seat yourself in it.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:50.19,1:36:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你会睡得很安稳{\r}\NYou're going to be comfortably put to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:53.80,1:36:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}只是一小段时间{\r}\NBut it'll last only for a short while.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:57.20,1:37:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}非常感谢你,你想得真周到{\r}\NThank you very much. You are most considerate.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:02.00,1:37:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}当你准备好后,让我知道{\r}\NLet me know when you're ready.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:04.91,1:37:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}顺便说一下,我还没看完那本书{\r}\NBy the way. I haven't quite finished that book...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:08.04,1:37:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你让我看书真好{\r}\Nyou were kind enough to let me have.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:10.41,1:37:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我想…能让我带走吗?{\r}\NMay I, uh, take it along?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:15.98,1:37:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好带走我们的指纹?{\r}\NWith our fingerprints on it? Tsk, tsk, tsk.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:18.39,1:37:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不错的尝试,阁下{\r}\NNice try, Your Excellency.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:21.56,1:37:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}谢谢,不烦你了,我准备好了{\r}\NThank you. Don't bother, then. I'm ready.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:26.76,1:37:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好的,我会把你的灯熄灭{\r}\NAll right, I'll be turning your light off now.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:55.32,1:37:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们不能迟到,看看是谁,小心点{\r}\NWe mustrt be late. See who it is, and be careful.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:29.42,1:38:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是她,那个女人,布兰琪・泰勒{\r}\N[Whispering] It's her. That woman. Blanche Tyler.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:32.66,1:38:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}简直难以置信!{\r}\N[Whispering] This is incredible!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:36.10,1:38:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 计程车司机和她在一起? - 只有她{\r}\N- Is that cab driver with her? - She's alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:41.44,1:38:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如果我不是要在35分钟内办事…{\r}\NIf I didn't have to make this pickup in 35 minutes...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:44.64,1:38:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们应该怎么做?{\r}\NWhat are we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:47.24,1:38:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}什么也别做!{\r}\NNothing!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:49.61,1:38:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}等一会儿{\r}\NUntil later tonight.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:04.29,1:39:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 她不见了 - 快点,走吧{\r}\N- She's gone. - Come on. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:07.13,1:39:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}快,快,快!{\r}\NHurry, hurry, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:33.25,1:39:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}(亲爱的亚当森先生){\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:35.25,1:39:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}(或者该称呼您休奎奇先生){\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:37.25,1:39:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}(请您回电给我){\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:39.25,1:39:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}(我有个天大的好消息要告诉你){\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:25.64,1:40:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我想你说过… - 我知道{\r}\N- I thought you said... - I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:28.61,1:40:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 亚当森先生? - 看着他{\r}\N- Mr. Adamson? - Watch him.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:38.15,1:40:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}喔,亚当森先生 真幸运,我没有错过你{\r}\NOh, Mr. Adamson. How lucky I am not to have missed you.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:42.22,1:40:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 显然你没有听到我在前门按铃 - 显然是{\r}\N- Apparently you didn't hear me at the front door. - Apparently.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:45.23,1:40:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我叫布兰琪・泰勒,是个通灵师{\r}\NI am Madame Blanche Tyler, the spiritualist.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:49.10,1:40:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}晚安,甜心{\r}\NGood evening, honey.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:51.43,1:40:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}布兰琪女士,我能麻烦你 把你的车移开我们的车道吗?{\r}\NMadame Blanche, I wonder if I might suggest to you to remove your car from our driveway.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:55.27,1:40:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我们约会快迟到了 - 喔,是的{\r}\N- We're terribly late for an appointment. - Well, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:58.24,1:41:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}当你听到我来的原因 亚当森先生…或者该称呼休奎奇?{\r}\NWhen you hear why I've come, Mr. Adamson... Or should I say Shoebridge?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:02.78,1:41:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你就不会介意迟到了 - 我亲爱的女士{\r}\N- You won't mind being late at all. - My dear lady,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:05.05,1:41:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我很清楚你来的原因 - 你怎么知道的?{\r}\N- I know exactly why you've come here. - How could you?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:07.25,1:41:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你和你的朋友,那个计程车司机… - 你认识乔治?{\r}\N- And exactly why you and your friend, that cab driver... - You know George?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:10.85,1:41:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}过去几个星期以来一直在追查我 就好像两条嗜血的猎犬{\r}\NHave been sniffing along my trail like two eager bloodhounds these past few weeks.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:16.02,1:41:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我没有这样想,亚当森先生{\r}\NI had no idea, Mr. Adamson.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:18.33,1:41:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 好吧,布兰琪女士,你找到我了 - 真是好极了{\r}\N- All right, Madame Blanche, you found me. - Music to my ears.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:21.56,1:41:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我非常愿意听取你的要求 不论是什么,但不是现在{\r}\NI'm perfectly willing to listen to your demands, whatever they might be, but not right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:26.33,1:41:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}没有要求,亚当森先生 噢,不,不,不{\r}\NNo demands, Mr. Adamson. Oh, no, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:29.40,1:41:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是几乎没有,朱莉亚・兰伯特 不会向你要求什么…{\r}\NHardly that. Julia Rainbird wants nothing from you...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:33.31,1:41:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但是你必须做她的继承人 继承所有兰伯特家的财富{\r}\Nbut the privilege of making you heir to the entire Rainbird fortune.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:38.05,1:41:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}所有的,动人的数百万美元{\r}\NThe whole, lovely millions and millions of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:40.28,1:41:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如果她有提出任何要求 那就是要我找到你{\r}\NNow if she made any demands at all, they were on me to find you.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:44.89,1:41:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}透过通灵的手段,那是当然的{\r}\NThrough psychic means, of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:47.92,1:41:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}让我搞清楚一下,这就是你和 你的朋友一直追查我的原因?{\r}\NLet me get this straight. Is that the only reason you and your friend have been,\Nshall we say, investigating me?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:52.86,1:41:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}喔,是的,不要以为这很容易{\r}\NOh, yes. And don't think it's been easy.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:55.53,1:41:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}噢,亚当森先生 你给了我和乔治魔鬼般的考验{\r}\NOh, Mr. Adamson, you've given George and me the devil's own time of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:58.97,1:42:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}追踪打从你婴儿时期被遗弃开始{\r}\NTracing you from a foundling baby...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:01.57,1:42:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}一直到叫做休奎奇的青年 然后是叫做亚当森的男士{\r}\Nto a young boy named Shoebridge to a man named Adamson.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:06.01,1:42:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}噢,但是,亚当森先生 你就在这里,我也在这里{\r}\NOh, but, Mr. Adamson, here you are, : Here I am.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:08.88,1:42:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这对我们来说 真是快乐的时刻,不是吗?{\r}\N- It's a happy moment for us all, isn't it? - [Fran Gasps]
Dialogue: 0,1:42:12.55,1:42:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是主教{\r}\N[Blanche] It's the Bishop. [Gasps]
Dialogue: 0,1:42:26.29,1:42:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}有谁知道你来这里?{\r}\NDoes anyone know that you've come here?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:30.10,1:42:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}没有人知道…{\r}\NNo one know...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:32.77,1:42:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}有谁会知道?{\r}\NAnyone kn-know?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:35.64,1:42:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不,连灵魂也没有{\r}\NNo. Not a soul.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:39.31,1:42:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}即使是乔治的灵魂{\r}\NNot even George soul.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:42.78,1:42:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你没有什么好担心的 亚当森先生{\r}\NYou have nothing to worry about, Mr. Adamson.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:47.72,1:42:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我保证{\r}\NI promise.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:52.35,1:42:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不会吐露半个字…给任何人{\r}\NI won't breathe a word... to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:15.88,1:43:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}看来布兰琪・泰勒女士 需要休息一下{\r}\NIt looks like Miss Tyler needs some rest.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:23.82,1:43:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你不听我的话?{\r}\NWill you do as I say?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:43.17,1:43:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不,不{\r}\NNo. No.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:29.08,1:44:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}打开门{\r}\NUnlock the door.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:38.96,1:44:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}高兴一点,法兰{\r}\NCheer up, Fran.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:40.96,1:44:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}让我们去取新的钻石 来装饰我们的吊灯吧{\r}\NLet's go get the new diamond for our chandelier.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:08.06,1:45:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}哇,真是漂亮{\r}\NWow. It's gorgeous.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:22.17,1:45:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}现在轮到布兰琪女士了{\r}\NAnd now for Madame Blanche.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:45.96,1:50:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}噢,我的天{\r}\NOh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:32.31,1:51:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}布兰琪?{\r}\NBlanche?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:45.69,1:51:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}布兰琪?{\r}\NBlanche?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:55.13,1:51:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}布兰琪?{\r}\NBlanche?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:26.86,1:52:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如果我说得太多 也许是因为你不说话{\r}\N[Adamson] If I'm talking too much, perhaps it's because you're not talking.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:31.03,1:52:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我胃痛,亚瑟,它不同意谋杀{\r}\NIt's my stomach, Arthur. Murder doesn't agree with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:34.33,1:52:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你以为我很期待?{\r}\NYou think I'm looking forward to it?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:36.97,1:52:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如果乔森・马洛尼能干一点 他们现在早就都死了{\r}\NIf Joe Maloney had been more efficient, they'd both be dead by now.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:41.68,1:52:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你可以拿走我的那一份,亚瑟{\r}\NYou can have my share, Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:44.34,1:52:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你可以把两颗钻石都占为己有 只要你能结束一切{\r}\NYou can keep both diamonds all to yourself if you'll just end it.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:49.85,1:52:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我会告诉你该怎么做{\r}\NI'll tell you what I'll do.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:52.65,1:52:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如果你帮我把这个睡美人 从地窖搬到我们的车上{\r}\NIf you help me carry Sleeping Beauty up out of the cellar, load her into our car...
Dialogue: 0,1:52:55.82,1:53:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}开车送她去荒芜的公路 那些可以自杀的地方{\r}\Nand drive her out to some deserted road where a suicide can take place,
Dialogue: 0,1:53:00.06,1:53:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我向你保证 我们可以来讨论这件事{\r}\NI promise you we'll talk this thing over.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:03.63,1:53:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 好吗? - 计程车司机怎么办?{\r}\N- Okay? - What about the cab driver?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:06.70,1:53:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如果她能找到我们 我相信他也可以{\r}\NIf she was able to find us, I'm sure he can too.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:11.07,1:53:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 他逃不出我们的手掌心 - 是你的手,不是我的{\r}\N- He'll walk right into our hands. - Your hands, not mine.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:15.84,1:53:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你不觉得我们 应该下去看一看她吗?{\r}\NDon't you think we ought to go down and take a look at her?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:18.35,1:53:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}自从我们给她注射以来 已经有一段时间了{\r}\NIt's been a while since we gave her that shot.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:20.51,1:53:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你去 - 好吧{\r}\N- You do it. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:37.69,1:54:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你会很高兴知道她仍然昏迷着{\r}\NYou'll be happy to know she's still unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:03.02,1:55:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 布兰琪 - 嘘{\r}\N[Whispers] - Blanche. - Shh!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:31.14,1:55:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我会这样结束,把管子的一端 接到排气管,另一端放在车窗中{\r}\NI'll put this end into her exhaust pipe...\Nand the other end in the window.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:37.62,1:55:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这样看来就像是自杀{\r}\NThat way, it'll look like suicide.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:15.02,1:56:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}最好现在就去把她带过来{\r}\NBetter go and get her now.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:17.26,1:56:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我要把她放在我们车里 你开她的{\r}\NI'll take her in our car. You follow in hers.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:33.64,1:56:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你抓住她的双脚{\r}\NYou take hold of her feet.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:40.55,1:56:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}老天,她还真重{\r}\NJesus, she's heavy. [Screaming]
Dialogue: 0,1:56:45.12,1:56:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}乔治!{\r}\NGeorge!
Dialogue: 0,1:56:48.62,1:56:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}抓到他们了{\r}\N[Panting, Coughing] Got 'em.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:54.39,1:56:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}布兰琪,你演的太好了{\r}\NBlanche, you faked that one beautifully.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:56.90,1:56:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你仍然是冠军{\r}\NYou are still the champ.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:59.87,1:57:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}谢谢,乔治{\r}\NThank you, George.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:02.44,1:57:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你知道这两个的赏金值多少吗?{\r}\NDo you realize how much the reward is for those two?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:07.51,1:57:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是的{\r}\N[Chuckling] Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:09.54,1:57:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但是你知道,如果我们能够 找到钻石,还会有多少奖励吗?{\r}\NBut do you realize how much more the reward would be...\Nif we could find the diamonds and turn 'em in?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:22.46,1:57:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你怎么了?{\r}\NWhat's the matter with you?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:25.29,1:57:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我…{\r}\NI...
Dialogue: 0,1:57:27.46,1:57:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}布兰琪,怎么回事?{\r}\NBlanche, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:40.61,1:57:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}布兰琪,怎么回事?{\r}\NBlanche, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:56.59,1:57:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}怎么了?{\r}\NWhat is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:29.06,1:58:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}布兰琪,你办到了!{\r}\NBlanche, you did it!
Dialogue: 0,1:58:31.59,1:58:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你真是个通灵师!{\r}\NYou are psychic!
Dialogue: 0,1:58:35.90,1:58:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我们在楼梯上干嘛? - 你不再是假的{\r}\N- What am I doing here on the stairs? - You're not a fake.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:38.73,1:58:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你真的找到了一个,瞧{\r}\NYou actually found one. Look.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:41.43,1:58:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我找到的?{\r}\NI did?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:43.44,1:58:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我要打电话给警察 告诉他们好消息{\r}\NI'll get the police on the phone and give them our good news,
Dialogue: 0,1:58:46.41,1:58:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}还要通知兰伯特女士 告诉她坏消息{\r}\Nand call Miss Rainbird and give her the bad.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:56.88,1:58:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}接线生,能帮我接通警察局吗?{\r}\NOperator, can I have the police?


